comments: ["I love this game, it's really good. But there's some glitches in the game, eg: on the path/road, you had to jump over it. It's really frustrating. I also lose coins sometimes, my progress is ruined. It's sad that Swift Apps doesn't care for this game anymore, they just abandoned it. In multiplayer it's really challenging to try beat other players as well. But thank you for making this game, it's my childhood. I would rate ★★★★☆.", "Its good, I like it. But it sucks that I always have to destroy stuff more to get to the next level, I couldn't even find the next level on level 4 . I don't wanna do time limits, to pass the level, I want it where I need to destroy everything to get 3 stars. Also, I would like to hit the people too. Has potential though, just more updates or fixing the controls, the only thing I hate about the controls is the camera view.", "This a really good game... But the game has a few glitches. ( Examples : in the first map you can get stuck in the walls...and the ladder you can get stuck in... ) ( And it fores you to buy a new dog. ) But it's all good other than that well... The controls are 'okay' I guess...you only get as a control button a attack button, a jumping button, and a go left, right, Forward, and back button. All the maps are good I had fun playing it. The first two maps are pretty good and easy. Enjoy", "I love the game and all, but there's one problem. I spent like 4 hours as a Great Collie running around and destroying stuff and finally getting 83k. When I changed region to join my brother, it all went away. This is very agitating. I still have my 153 gems, which is good. Overall, this game deserves 5 stars, even if I lost 4 hours of progress.", 'Really good but theres a bug im experiencing ( sorry if thats spelled wrong ) where some of the things you destroy are stuck in the ground ( barrels, hay stacks, crates, pumpkins, and tables in particular ) please do fix this! Also i would love it if there were more levels this game is really fun thanks for making it!', "I can't even describe how good it is! But the problem is it don't shows ur score to go to next lvl but it's ok anyway! I'll try to understand it soon! The controls are super easy, I always rage quit cuz big lvls always hit me xD and when I randomly join the garden we always go run and try to get in the house first till time runs up! XD I always play that xD it's a really good game!", "I love this app so much. It's kinda hard when you have to walk but its the best simulator I've ever had. I love the new places u can go and the challenges. Love this game. Hope you people like it too. And you get different dogs anytime. And love wrecking houses and etc.", 'I love this app! The controls are so easy! I rated 4 stars because you still have to fix one thing. When you get off your device for 7 minutes then get back on your device it freezes a little bit.', "It is really bad until it really spoils my mood when playing this game. 1.you don't show the score that we need to beat in order to go to the next round. 2.why does the dog needs to jump over the thing on the road when it is not that high. 3. sometimes there is point & sometimes don't when you hit the thing. 4. I already pressed the jump button for so many times, the dog just stucked there & couldn't go up. Please fix those problems as soon as possible. It is good game but bad quality.", "I love this game! It's cute, fun, and addicting! You get to play and act as a real dog and you can destroy stuff in every place that you visit! It has cool maps and other kinds of dogs, too! It has great graphics and is entertaining! It's one of the best games I tried out, including the Cat Simulator I just rated! I also love dogs because they're cute and playful! Thank you guys for making this game! I think you made my day today! 🐶👍", 'Well this is a fun game but when I saw the game wanted to rate this game and when I looked at the "no" sign the puppy was sad. I couldn\'t handle that pain so I said "yes" This game was fun but there are a few bugs that when I jump anywhere i get stuck at objects. Also all the humans and dog furs are blurred with bad texture. But it\'s good anyways 👌🏻', 'ITS SO COOL!!! I love dogs and thats just what this game is!!! Simply by being a cute pup! I wish you would add a trick button so when you press it the dog would do something like Sitting, roll over, back flip, bark(speak), and even play dead... And the people will react to the puppy and if they like it you will get +2 coins every time they like it so please and that update and u can add some more dog tricks if you do add it so yeah... Thats all! bye..!', "Fun and addictive. I decided to install this on a whim with my boyfriend. Although there are many ads, this game is fun to kill time and spread happiness. Sometimes it is a bit buggy and you're unable to jump up though.", "been playing since like 2015 (on and off) and oh my god it's so addicting and nostalgic, I come back to it every now and then for a nostalgia trip and stay for the fun. 10/10 game even though others might not agree. the stupid (ADORABLE) unity asset dogs make me happy beyond words and I honestly dont even know why", 'This is a very adorable game! I love the text that pops up and the achievements. There are many levels that humans come in every day! Anyways the dogs all have great fur colors,Graphics and cuteness! I would recommend this to any dog lover!', "It's a very good game but I would like it if there animals were cheaper and i always had i problem that it says I'm disconnected but it plays me an add... yeah dont get it... I love this game and the other ones pls dont make me uninstall it and lose everything just to play it again to play online and just do the same thing...", "very very good game the background is amazing and the concept of the game that is to destroy everyrhing is the best part but i would suggest you to have some more levels so that the game is long and fun and you should add 'choose your background music' feature", 'I like this app cause,im a dog lovers!! If anyone wanted like to be a dog? Like uh i dont know how to explain but this game is for a dog lover! The reason i give ☆☆☆☆ Stars is because sometimes when you jump the dogs/puppies they will like stuck at the floor so you have to restart it! Its just so annoying! Even when you are on a Quest lik the timer and yea..its pretty diffrent from cat simulator but,i like cat simulator more even tho im a dog lovers but like..Dude,fix your game..', "Best dog game ever But there's 1 issue. Can you please make it to where the dog can run fully and knock over tables and stuff, not glitch and turn ? It's like that for my bro too. Pls make an update. When we run and knock stuff over outside and inside, it makes us turn back or we glitch and turn, It's glitched. u just need to make an update to fix the problem pls. Then I'll give it 5 stars. And share with my friends. I got other update idea. Can u PLS make a chat box so we can chat with people.", "The concept and quality of the game is great. But be aware that if you play often enough online, you can just like any other multiplayer game, you'll notice toxic players and possibly even a literal demonic encounter. And you'd think this game is for little kids. This game, like other multiplayer games, are NOT for Christians at all! So all in all if you are a good person, be aware of playing on multiplayer everyday. Multiplayer should be removed. Can't run anarchy with such a despicable world.", "It has such great graphics if you like something simple it is a little weird with the humans faces but that's fine it's just that they are a little flat but other than that it's a really nice game and you should get it's for your kids if they really like dogs and they like simulators", 'Very good over all! Cool levels, Many "Combos" and much more. But, sometimes my game has a bug. Please fix this. But overall, it\'s a good game. You should atleast try it', 'I love the levels but please add more. It is so fun that we get to destroy, but, the stuff costs to much I had 2000 coins and gems I had to get stuff for my pup. After I did that, I had 10 coins, and 12 gems. Please fix it.', 'Fun game its a good game cant stand the rotation of the screen love it but theres some stuff thats missing like how do you know how many points you need to get to unlock one map or land. Please update that for now i uninstalled its not bad maybe a 2-3 is a good rating for this game hopefully soon it will be 5 stars game thank you for reading my request ♡.', 'Wonderful game! 10/10 It does glitch sometimes, but almost every game does. Super fun, easy to learn, and you can even use it to relieve stress!', "It is so awesome I can't stop playing and I love to ruin things like a store because I going to the store and I love dogs.You should try this game if you like this game you should play it more often if you don't like the game just find a game that is a good fit for you.Don't forget to share with friends!!!!", "Good game I used to play this when I was four and five years old now I'm 9 in a corder and I still love this game it brings back memories of when I was little thank you so much for making this game now I have to get used to the controls again😂 because I haven't played this in so long lol🤭🤣🤣🥰 keep up on the good work,!!!!!!!😍😉", "It's a very great game.But the dogs are too much expensive...and the graphics are awesome! I want more places..and make the dogs less the gems and money...I wish you could add more in this game in the future so more people will install this great game!", "It's cute and fun. Not at all different from the cats one. Just with dogs instead. You still jump around and knock down and break things. That's more of a cat thing, so seeing dogs jump up a counter and knock stuff down is kinda weird.", "It's overall a fun game to play, you will get addicted to it. However, it would be nice to have the option to switch the joypad for both left handed and right handed. I suck at this game and find it difficult to move the dog around with my left thumb as my a right handed", "It's a nice time killer and it's great for when you have nothing better to do. There's not many maps and they're easy to unlock. It took me less than an hour to go through the entirety of it. Maybe add some more maps.", "It's really fun but the reason I put 4 stars is that it takes a while to get on the next level in the shop level still a really good game though also make the ladder easier to climb up and make the dogs cheaper please", "The graphics are terrible. It is these games that use a timer and in the game I can't even jump instead I get frozen in mid air. Soo cheap.", "My kids love this game so I think it's the best game for my kids Even though my kids loved it I tried this game and it's actually really fun so I think everybody out there should try it yeah totally Chivas game is about it. Awesome dogs they did really bad things that I can sit love this game so whatever", 'I like this game but there is no missions no more places to go to you should really update the game so it can have more features', 'Amazing reflexes, quality, and graphics! Its cool because you can releaar your stress and smash stuff XD and you can play with friends and have a lot of fun! 💜💜😀', "It's a really fun game you get to choose many cute puppies and smash everything just to make humans regret this and just for them to get furious but when I installed this game from yesterday they have levels and without the challenge all your coins first get higher then lower for some reasons of give it a five star if you remove the challenge thing its irritating me plus I uninstalled it sadly 😒", 'Although you have not fixed the breaking objects dissapearing and never coming back, items being broken as you enter a level and items being driven into the ground and will launch you into the air if you try to knock it over at a certian angle -_-', "Love the game, however I'm stuck at level 3 and I am not sure of what am I supposed to do or even what objects to wreck. So far I am getting a high score but not a star. Therefore I have no clue what I should be doing/what score do I need to move to level 4.", 'The game is fun and the graphics is great!...But I rated it three stars because when we create a custom game it dont have a password and other players join in...And by the way they always punch us and im pissed of them... Could you make a password please...Thank you']

title: Dog Hotel Tycoon
description:
Become a dog hotel tycoon, and create a world for your dog guests to enjoy!

CREATE A WORLD FOR YOUR DOG GUESTS TO ENJOY!
Start with a small dog hotel in a suburban area, and improve it to become the first 5+ star dog hotel! Create areas for your dogs to take naps, eat delicious snacks, play with each other, swim, excercise and much more! Anything to ensure the satisfaction of your dog guests!

WELCOME DOGS FROM ALL AROUND THE WORLD!
Become a dog hotel tycoon and accept more breeds as you grow your hotel, such as Corgi, Dachshund, Pug, Samoyed, Poodle, German Shepherd, Labrador, French Bulldog, English Bulldog, Basset Hound, Chiuahua, Chow Chow, Beagles, Shiba Inu, and many more. Each and every single dog will have their own unique character, behavior, wants and needs; and it is up to you to satisfy them!

TAKE YOUR DOGS TO DAILY DOG EVENTS!
Each day, you'll be able to take your dogs to the daily Dog Show, which is a physical obstacle challenge that will test the health & fitness of your dogs! 
There will also be a new Dog Quiz waiting for you each day, which will test your knowledge about dogs as well as teaching you interesting facts about them!

FEATURES
★ Easy to play game for every animal lover!
★ Cute Dogs with unique characteristics and lifelike behavior!
★ More than 80 dogs to have as guests, and more to come!
★ Fun rooms and items for your dogs to enjoy!
★ Send your dogs to Dog Shows!
★ Learn about dogs and earn rewards with the daily Dog Quiz!

If you love dogs, and incremental idle clicker games, you will love idle Dog Hotel Tycoon. As with all idle clicker games, you will never run out of things to do!

This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any issues with the game or have any feedback, you can always reach us at support@filgames.com
summary: Become a dog hotel tycoon, and create a world for your dog guests to enjoy!

title: Dog Game - The Dogs Collector!
description:
With cute art and adorable mini-games, you’ll be caring for your puppies in Dog Game any chance you get! Thousands have given Dog Game two furry paws up! 🐾

Dog Game is simple yet highly-addictive! To play, all you need to do is collect different kinds of cute & unique dogs and build a home for them, your very own Dog Tower! You can craft decoration and create lovely rooms to unlock cute new puppies to fill them with every single day.

Collect adorable dogs like shiba inu, husky, pug, bulldog, golden retriever and beagle! There’s over 900 puppys you can collect! 💫 Decorate rooms in your dog towers with your favourite styles: unicorn, fancy, legendary, anime, magic and so many more!


🌟 DOG GAME HIGHLIGHTS

● 900+ kawaii puppies to collect!
● Watch your animals come to life with cute animations
● Craft furniture and decorate your dream Dog Tower
● Play special events and earn exclusive pups & prizes
● Enter contests to design the most adorable rooms
● Play fun & addictive mini-games to earn coins
● Join a club & play with your friends (and make new ones)
● Compete in the leaderboard for exclusive rewards
● Daily missions & contests!
● There’s something new every week!


🏠 DECORATE YOUR OWN PUPPY TOWER

Create & personalize an adorable dog tower for all of your puppies to live in! Craft adorable decorations like plants, couches, dog toys, windows, sandcastles and adorable animal furniture.

You will adopt dogs of different themes and vibes according to your own taste! 70’s, beach, dance club, farm, underwater, or royalty. 


💖 PLAY GAMES WITH FRIENDS

Dog Game is a great pet game to play with friends! You can enter contests where you compete by designing the best dog room! You will play with dog lovers across the world! Dog Game is an amazing way to make new friends and socialize in new clubs!

Enter fun events throughout the year where you can earn unique rare dogs and special prizes! Unlock new challenging levels by playing minigames! 

Participate in non-stop dog-themed games like:
● BarckyBlocks: Match blocks like in tetris and beat all high scores
● PuppyPops: Match adorable dogs and earn lots of coins
● Spin the Basket
● And more!


✨ YOUR VIRTUAL PET AWAITS YOU IN DOG GAME

Your future pups are waiting for you now! Put your paws to work, play with friends & clubs, and get Dog Game today for free!

comments: ['Been playing this game for over a year and have really enjoyed it. Recently though, the events are just reskins of either floors from Cat Game or repeats of already past events. While a little repeat is to be expected, it just seems like they stopped caring about working on this game. Getting to the point where I am done with the regular tower and there are no options to continue, unless I spend actual money. Getting a little disappointed, because it is a fun game most times.', "This app won't work properly for me. I downloaded it, chose my starter dog, then it went to the house and the only thing it showed was the floor and the dog I chose. No tutorial. I thought it was just like that and I've played the cat game, so I fed her and even got two decos as well as the next dog. But I ran out of food and nothing. I couldn't do anything. So I closed the app and got back in and it restarted. From the beginning where you choose the dog.", "I've played dg for 2 yrs and cg for 1 yr. Lately cg has become unplayable due to lag. I worry the same will happen here after having invested thousands of hrs and $. Dog Game lacks some features from Cat Game & the crafting + leveling is overall more difficult. It lacks a full VIP reward system as well. My biggest issue is with player support. Often we feel ignored with our feedback & concerns. We know we won't get help from certain support staff. Bugs are left unfixed & there is no compensation", 'Really great game with awesome drawings. The one thing that I would complain about is the ads; right after you play a mini game,it just gives you a pop-up ad. I believe this is similar to the cat game, so if you are interested in the game, this game will surely spark your interest.', "Great game! I really love it and I enjoy it. I think it runs smoothy and it's really fun to collect dogs. I do have one thing that bothers me. Recently I've been having to uninstall and reinstall the game because it keeps glitching. Whenever I load the game up and I'm waiting in the loading screen once it gets to 100% the dog glitches out and then my screen goes black. Nothing happens after that and it's been happening recently. I hope this can get fixed. It's still a great game, love it!", "Cute and fun time waster about collecting dogs! I haven't been able to put it down! For such a simple concept it sure is fun. It's a bit money hungry but not overly so. A purchase removes ads, at least. They are generous with premium currency so that's always a plus. It would be nicer if there were more than 2 mini games to earn coins, though. Overall I'm happy with this game. The dogs are super cute, there are a ton of different ones (real and fantasy) and the wait times are not that bad!", "The cuteness can't be denied, and I love how every dog has their own unique animation - that makes the collecting all the more worthwhile! My main gripe is that advancing depends heavily on crafting, which takes a good amount of both resources and coins, which are hard to earn with only two mini games. There's a whole lot of waiting involved (wait for boxes to be delivered, wait for food options to be refreshed, wait for crafting to be completed) and the minigames are both pretty short plays.", "I really love the game but I've recently started having issues with booting the game up. It will load the start screen and once it starts loading, it give me a black screen and I can no longer play it. I've uninstalled and reinstalled it a couple of times and it loads my save, vut after a few times of playing, it give me the dreaded black screen again. Not sure who to contact because the black screen won't really allow me to contact anyone. 😕", "Recently it's just been glitching out at the loading screen and going black. I've been trying for a week or so now just to get loaded into the game, but it will instead freeze up and sometimes make me restart my phone entirely. It was fun for a bit, I guess, and I like it more than CG because I'm a dog person... but it is quite literally unplayable.", "This is my updated review! It took a few trys to actually get the game to the point where i had a game id and it would save my progress. The game is addicting but you have to be lucky with the spins in the beginning to actually be able to move on. Its not a problem after you get past the tutorial part but in the beginning if you keep getting dogs then you don't have enough supplies to continue and you have to start over. This needs to be fixed for future players! It is still a pretty fun game!", "its awsome! i love it so cute the one thing that bothers me is when you get a puppy it comes in a basket and when you get to a higher level it take soo long to get out of the basket but it isn't to big of a problem so i still give it five stars its a very fun game so i recomend it its very cute i play it so much", "I really love the game:) 1. No issues 2 . No laggy stuff 3. Not a lot of ads 4.Really fun and colorful 5.a lot of reskins from cat game but I don't mind", "After continuously getting the black screen when trying to load, I deleted the game then re-installed it. It worked! But now it's doing the same thing AGAIN. I'm missing another event because of these issues, and I did very much enjoy the game. This whole situation, however, is really souring my opinion and enjoyment, ESPECIALLY due to the developers' lack of action and response.", "I LUV it!!! It's SOOO cute and fun. I very rarely rate 5 starts so be proud of yourself! Very underrated! I don't even get pop up adds! 100% recomend! Update: I'm changing my rating. Its not letting me play anymore. Only thing I can do is click the play button. I can hear the music but after I click the play button it brings me to a black screen and nothing happens. Just the music playes. Pls fix.", "It's cute but it gets old doing the same two mini games over and over to earn coins. And sometimes when you watch an ad, it completely freezes the game (sometimes my phone too) and then crashes. Also the percentage of landing a dog the further you go is annoying. I want to continue to get more rooms, not collect an over amount of materials.", "the game doesn't work. it makes me restart the game every time and it doesn't show anything but the dogs. no tutorial or menu. nothing.", 'I love this game, from the art to the gameplay its highly addictive. I do suggest it to everyone, as a dog lover i love every piece of it! To the devs thank you so much for making it. Have a nice day', "This game is super fun to play casually when you need something to do. The mini games are super user friendly and super helpful when you need some coins. The crafting section is great, but my only complaint is that it takes a while to get a dog in any room, and my barbecue room has a huge amount of cotton before there's even a chance you can get a dog. Other than that, not disappointed!☺️", "The game is cute. Its just as fun as cat collector, which I've played for almost 3 years now. But this one has too any ads! After each round of game play there is an ad before you get your coins. Ger rid of that please! There is a glitch in the doggopedia, I can't see most of my dogs, and when I scroll through it, it doesn't work correctly. Each time I deliver a basket or feed for supplies, instead of going back where I was, I'm taken to the top of the tower. It's just frustrating.", "Crafting recipes are so difficult. Would definitely like to see them be changed to be like Cat Game's recipes. An option to permanently opt out of global chat (CG got this recently) would be amazing. I think the % chance of getting a dog is a lie, feels like I have to wait and spin so many times before I get one. I love this game, I'm enjoying it even more than CG (that I've played for 2+ years and am almost max level on). With a few tweaks, I think it'll be perfect!", "This game has been a lot of fun so far. The dogs are super cute and my 4yr old daughter absolutely loves them all. Problem now is that the game was asking me to update, but it hasn't 😕 had the spinning circle the entire day. Tried resetting my phone, nothing. Tried turning it off then back on, nothing. I even tried Uninstalling to see if that would work but now it won't even let me re-install! 🥺 Please help fix this bug!", "This game is sooo cute!! I definitely recommend it. It does have very few ads, but it can take a really long time to get a basket. Otherwise, It's very fun!", "Amazing game! I love the designs and animations, foods are cute. I love every dog and I'm attached to all of them! I just hate the fact that you have to wait for a very very long time because then I either have to do random stuff for the long time on the game or just leave and go back later which annoys me a bit. Good game overall though", 'i loved cat game so much even though i\'m a dog person so obviously i\'m super into dog game! it really is the best. (1.) it\'s calming without being boring. (2.) you never run out of things to do, but there\'s no stressful feeling of like "ugh it\'s too much work." (3.) there\'s mini games! and the adorable dog home decor challenges? ugh yes, so fun! (4.) the mini games are actually fun and you get coins for playing them. i\'d love a unicorn version in the future!', "Very cute game. I love this game and CG, but I play this more since I'm more of a dog person than a cat person. The only real issue I have with it is that sometimes the loading gets stuck at around 55%, and I have to restart the app to get back to the home screen. The premium keys aren't very easy to get as the only way is through completing floors, and it would be great if you could add the ability to add friends and private messages!", "Recently been having issues with the game loading, I get a blank screen with music playing. I've tried on two separate phones and tried re-downloading it. When it does finally load it works for a few minutes and then crashes. Seems to be an issue for a lot of people right now, so hoping it can be fixed soon.", "I really liked it to start. Got all the way to level 23 and suddenly got stuck on a black screen. I uninstalled and reinstalled and had to start all over. Support says they can't help me because the game added random numbers to the end of my screenname and I don't know them. Started all over and now it's stuck on the black screen again when I try to open it. I think I'm done.", "I enjoy this game a lot, super cute and fun to play, I love the different themes :) Edit: As I level up, the chances are becoming too low, and collecting is difficult. I'm only level 15 - hope to see some tweaks in this area as the game has so much potential!", "It's basically the cat game, but with dogs! I've loved the cat game since my friend introduced me to it a few years ago, and when my sibling brought this to my attention I couldn't pass up the opportunity to play. Aside from minor stylistic changes it's the same; so it's perfect to play when I'm waiting on things to craft in the cat game (and vice versa) While it seems a little odd to have the same themes as paid for floors in the cat game be free in this one, that's really the only flaw imo", "Very annoying. After waiting for a few months for it to catch onto some of CG's better qualities and not just compile its worst the game only presented a black screen every time I attempted to log into it. For two days, everytime I tried to get into the heart of the app this happened. Since I know the first thing is always suggested to Uninstaller and reinstall, I did that and the game started me over and says backup and restoring can't be done. What a waste.", 'Definitely a super fun game. Crafting is a little harder than Cat Game but still really fun. Great support too. They just restored both of my accounts after having to get a new phone and not being able to get back into my old Google Play account. The only thing I wish they would allow is for us to be able to gift more than 10 items at a time to club members requesting items.', "Was looking for a cute collection game with a very specific want for a clean colorful style, and this + cat game fits the bill very well. I like to support games I'm fond of so I've allowed myself to purchase ONE floor from each, and otherwise haven't felt compelled to purchase anything at all to proceed. I do wish there were more mini games I admit, a simple endless runner I believe would go over really well, but all in all a lot of fun, can't complain!", "I wrote this review on the cat alternative so I figured I'd mention it here too. It's an amazing game but there are some wifi troubles. It could just be me but for both games I have to frequently switch my wifi on and off because you need wifi to play but the game won't load when it's on. Sometimes you need wifi to do things and sometimes you can play offline perfectly fine which is weird. Other than that it's sooo adorable and I highly recommend it!!", "Also having the black screen after the loading as others are reporting. A little disappointed that it's right in the middle of an event and more disappointed now that I may get auto-booted from my club before this gets fixed. I'm really trying to hang in there because I enjoy Cat Game so much, but it's getting very difficult.", "An inferior version of Cat Game, which is a shame cause I really love the cute dogs as well. Crafting is such a nightmare though - both regular and events. It's not nearly as much of a slog to get through levels twice as high up as the ones in my little dog tower. Feels like they want you to spend money to move faster but nah. I'd get more for my money from their own other product.", "Changed my rating. We had to get to like the 4th floor before we were able to quit the game and have it save. My son and I both downloaded this. Played it a bunch. I got to the second level with 2 dogs when I stopped playing. Next time I went into the game, all my progress was gone except the original dog that I picked. The same thing happened with my son. I love the cat game and had high hopes for this one. If you fix the bug, I'll gladly change my rating.", "Hi! I've been playing dog game for a few months now, but suddenly the app started closing on me and now after the loading screen it goes dark and won't open the game. I've Uninstalled it and reinstalled it, it connected to my account, and again the same problem. I'd contact support, but if I can't open the app I'm not sure how to contact support. Any idea why this is happening or how I can fix it? Thanks in advanced!", "Ever since the update I can't play the game. I LOVED playing it. The update has caused the game to no load. The start screen comes up, press the start button, says its loading to 55% then it just goes black and nothing else happens. I'm super upset because I love playing the game but now I'm also missing out on the events that are going on. Really hoping this gets fixed fast.", 'I play "Cat Game" as well this game is just as cute and is easy to play, however it\'s not as convenient as "Cat Game". I don\'t like the way hearts cannot be collected in one tap and expire too quickly. It takes up too much space on the club screen and messes with our club\'s ability to chat.', "900 dogs and no Index to keep track! ...... I started to play the game and it seemed okay .... Then, upon getting my first 'epic' dog I went to look for it but couldn't find it. I then realized that ALL dogs appear as the same level once opened. I searched for some type of index to differentiate the dogs but nothing. I informed the support team and they said there was no such option in the game. Absolute fail."]

title: Panda Games: Pet Dog Life
description:
Welcome to the Pet Dog Home! Are you ready to begin a cozy house life with your dogs? Adopt dogs, take care of them and play with them!

ADOPT DIFFERENT DOGS
14 adorable dogs of different breeds and colors are waiting for you to adopt. Each dog has its own personality! Adopt your favorite dogs and live in the pet dog home with them! There are surprises in every corner of the cabin!

TAKE CARE OF PET DOGS
The dogs' day starts with a delicious breakfast! Add dog food, and feed them well! After playtime, give your dog a nice bubble bath! Don't forget to monitor their health and treat the sick ones!

DRESS UP CUTE DOGS
Now, open your closet and dress your dog in cute clothes! First, let's wear a cape for your dog and then pick a nice bib for it. Last, put on a cozy little hat for your dog! Done! Your dog looks even cutter now!

PLAY WITH DOGS
There are so many toys that you can play with your dogs: frisbee, swing, and more! Play with your dogs in any way you like at the pet dog home! This will bring you closer together. Try different fun mini-games and exercise your brain while playing!

Download Panda Games: Pet Dog Life and spend some fun time with your dogs in the pet house!

FEATURES:
- 14 cute dogs available for adoption;
- Feed, bathe, dress up and take care of your dogs;
- Explore the Pet Dog House: living room, bedroom and playhouse;
- Plenty of dog toys: tennis, swing and frisbee;
- Many fun mini-games to play with your dogs;
- Supports offline mode！

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 400 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

—————
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

title: Bumble: Dating App & Friends
description:
Welcome to Bumble 💛 The community with millions of people where you can find dates, make new friends, and meet people.

Bumble is a free dating app and social network for singles; the perfect place to meet new people, in an instant. Whether you want to find friends, make genuine matches, find meaningful connections, chat with strangers, make new friends, or even expand your professional and social network, we’ve got you covered.

Changing the rules of dating

Bumble is a free dating app (to download and use) founded on respect, equality, and inclusion. You can find dates, meet up, and meet new people the way you've always done — but on Bumble, women always make the first move. You won’t find that on any other dating apps. 🕒 With heterosexual matches, women have 24h to start a chat, and men have 24h to respond 💬 Other matches (LGBTQIA+) have 24h to start a chat or reply before the match expires 👥 Bumble comes in 3 modes to suit what you're looking for: Date, BFF, and Bizz

Discover our amazing features

Meet new people, make new friends, or find a great date using our free dating app. We’ve levelled up from the days of dating sites, and now you have all these features at your fingertips: 👉 Unlimited Swipe: Meet new people by swiping left and right as much as you like 💬 Unlimited chat so you can find the right matches 🎵 Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends 📹 Use Video Chat to get to know your matches better

Match with the right people

We're the first app to combine dating for singles, meeting new people, and making professional connections all in one app. We’re different from other dating apps, because we make it easy for you to connect. 📹Use Video Chat to get to know your matches better 📷 Send your videos and favorite pictures while you are chatting with new friends 💤 With Snooze Mode, hide your profile whenever you want (you'll still keep all your matches!) 🎵 Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends

Boost your dating life with Bumble Premium

Bumble is a free dating app to download and use, and always will be! Our Premium features help you enhance your Bumble experience. 💛 See everyone who swiped right on you (your Beeline) 🔁 Rematch with expired connections for a second chance at a date 🔄 Extend your matches by 24 hours The buzz is real Bumble is much more than just a dating app for singles, or your average speed dating night. Join our like-minded dating community, meet new people, find your ideal partner or date. Here are our core values: 💛 We believe healthy relationships are fundamental to living a productive and positive life 💛 In the fight against old-fashioned hetero-norms, women always take the first step. 💛We've changed the rules of the game to switch up the dynamics of dating 💛Unlike other dating apps, kindness is at the core of everything we do Inclusivity is key We’re committed to being totally inclusive, and supportive of our community whatever their gender, sexual orientation, or religion. Whether you’re looking for a place to find friends, a gay dating app, a bisexual dating app, a lesbian dating app, an LGBTQ dating app, a Christian dating app or a Jewish dating app; We’ve got everything you’re looking for in our lovely community. --- Bumble is a dating app that is free to download and use. We also offer optional subscription packages (Bumble Boost and Bumble Premium) and non-subscription, single, and multi-use paid features (Bumble Spotlight and Bumble SuperSwipe). Your personal data is securely stored on Bumble - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions https://bumble.com/en/privacy https://bumble.com/en/terms Bumble Inc. is the parent company of Bumble, along with the dating apps Badoo and Fruitz. Enjoy all our dating apps!

comments: ["Its definitely a good app, but could use a few improvements. I don't use premium, but I don't mind it much so far. Anyhow, I do find it irritating that women always have to make the first move. I get why Bumble chose to do so, but it's irritating I always have to text first, especially since matches expire. Sometimes I get busy or forget to check the app, and I lose a lot of matches. I think it'd be nice sometimes if the other person could also text first.", "It is a total waste of time and money. It does not matter if you have premium, you won't be receiving any matches at all (I had subscribed to the premium, still the same). It's like a window shopping app where you just keep scrolling and scrolling until you're satisfied without hoping to get anything. For once I thought this app could be genuine and I purchased the premium, but no, if all I had to do was left and right swipe people, I might have as well stayed on Tinder for free.", 'Waste of time and money, the location of people is totally hit and miss, when you do "match" with someone it is debatable if they are actually real or generated by the app to keep you interested. For an app that is meant to compliment your social circle/find people with similar interests and so on, no one actually talks. Might just stick with the old-fashioned way!', 'The UI is quite user friendly. But few things which can be improved on. 1. Message notification doesn\'t pop up a lot of times 2. Call notification doesn\'t pop up ever, plus call drops multiple times 3. Filter option doesn\'t work properly, for example if I choose age range 33-36, I still see people of age 23 4. Algo for common interest can be improved specially for best bees feed, I get best bees who want "Something Casual" while my preference is "Relationship"', 'I can not escape the feeling of a jacked up algorithm. One that puts people on the bottom despite their subscription in some sort of "lead with a carrot" business model. That or no one\'s on this app, and the app does not seem to want to take people who have not been on the app in months in the algorithm. Furthermore, there seems to be no quick, obvious, and easy way to end your subscription.', "I used the app for about one year and had a few decent dates out of it. However, as soon as my paid membership expired, literally overnight, I went from having zero people interested in me to 47, of course being prompted to go back to the paid version. Didn't change location or filters during that time, so obviously, they are manipulating the truth and the end user.", 'For an app that requires access to your location, you\'d think they\'d give you an accurate mileage estimate for people near you, but nope they can\'t be bothered to do that. Just saw someone who lives in the next state over from me and, according to Bumble, they\'re 85 miles away from me. However, when I enter the city on Google maps, it gives me a much more accurate mileage: 156 miles. That\'s a 71 mile difference, nearly double Bumble\'s "estimate."', 'The worst of all dating apps. Like Tinder, gives you options from ridiculous distances, especially if youre in rural areas. Most people are visitors from very far. The worst part is once youve swiped left on a potential match they are removed from your likes and you probably will never see them again."you\'ve missed a potential match" forever. Also they put the location at the bottom so you have to scroll the whole profile just to see the distance factor. Overall a very bad experience', "This app is ok but needs work. I canceled my premium. One of the big thing that must be added is letting me know when the last time a person logged on. That way I'm not wasting time on someone who hasn't logged on in a month. That's a waste of a swipe especially a super swipe. Also need to separate straight people from gay. As I have swiped on the wrong person and they get all offended. If these things were fixed I would keep logging in.", "Terrible app! you have to pay for basic Things like just to see who liked you you can only see the people that complimented your profile and that's limited, You have to pay for everything like super swipes & to go back if you made a mistake. They took down one of my photos for going against community guide lines but it's a picture of me in a long dress no nudity nothing inappropriate. & whatever preferences youre allowed to choose (age and distance) doesn't narrow down the field", "Still an awful app, I've tried it multiple times and men never see their related matches. We get search results from 97 miles away from people who don't match our criteria. And you can tell even from the blurry images that you never see the people who actually do swipe on you. It's entirely designed to keep you swiping without any actual results. Don't waste your time", 'It\'s just as bad if not worse than Tinder surprisingly. Customer service is 0/10. I can\'t get a hold of any humans to discuss my problems, I\'ve sent at least 10 emails. I get photos randomly taken down because they "violate" community standards according to the algorithm. I\'ve purchased the lifetime membership twice and, like anyone, deleted and reinstalled the app many times, but now I dont have the lifetime membership, and they won\'t fix it. Summary: All dating apps suck.', "I think it's more likely to get struck by lightning and win the lottery at the same time than get a match. It's way too easy to accidentally swipe left, and those swiped on can't come back, and the highlights cost 8 bucks each. Like, who even? Fix your app.", "What's the use of having the dating interface if you can't even contact/connect to a prospect without having to pay a bloody fee? And even then, even if you do want to spend on it, the chances of getting catfished is unbelievably high. The aspect of this side of the app is completely useless. I will give it props if you're using it for business networking purposes and works well if that is your ONLY objective. The dating interface is bonkers.", "it's very picky and decisive wanting you to spend money just like any other app. they shouldn't just give the option free to connect with anyone but they should make a lot easier if you want to say hello or block or do what you would like explicit or not. there's filters for everything. just make it all around app that everybody can use. it's 2023 and this is the longest run on sentence I've ever done. but we all know what we're looking for in the beginning and in the end and who may b in middle", "All the other dating apps I get plenty of matches, but bumble is awful at what it's supposed to do. No matches, and because of the time limit to message you often miss the matches you do get. Pointless app and a waste of time. Edited, after the reply I received more likes than before after I left a review, strange, then they started to get less and Ive just realised the compliment feature has been removed. I think the free compliments were the only thing that made bumble worth using.", "Because you can't filter results by important categories like religion without paying, the app is essentially useless. You are forced to weed through thousands of profiles that aren't close to your value specifications. The profiles layout is also a mess, listing interests in a buckshot-style jumble where things like children, religion, age, location, etc are thrown into the mix randomly and you have to look around more to find it (those should be at the top of the list).", 'Totally wast of time & Money, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "It's...ehhh. My issues are the inability to filter out poly/ENM profiles looking for unicorns, continuing to get likes from men when I am a lesbian, the constant message ads and empty notifications, and the high cost of premium. Been using it for a few months now, met one potential person but I'm demoralized. I won't renew my subscription.", "Bumble is useless without a premium subscription. All filters except age & distance are now locked behind a paywall, so rooting through all the bad matches to find someone is a chore. You only get 24 hours to respond to a match, otherwise you have to pay to rematch. And if you accidentally swipe left on someone you do want to match with, you have to pay to undo it. If the woman matches but doesn't start chatting within 24 hours, (Something that happens A LOT) the match disappears completely.", "The customer service for Bumble is absolutely terrible!! I have contacted them over 10 times in a two week span and Bumble has not replied to ANY of my inquiries. My account is stuck on photo verification and I cannot access any othet part of my account. I am currently paying for the Premium option as well. Don't use this app - they dont care about you at all.", "Not sure how I feel about it. So far I like how the verification process goes and the app runs smooth but been on it for 2 weeks with premium and not worth it. You don't really get as much people due to the fact that the premium is expensive and also the notification when you do get someone doesn't really appear on either the app notification or email. Also anyone you've liked you can't tell if they even seen the like. Definitely needs more work for the cost.", "I like this app, in my opinion it' s very nice but it's just ridiculously expensive. probably the most expensive app I've tried. so I subscribed in different app although I still use the free features on Bumble. Some things could be better. don't like the fact that only match girls can do first move, think that's silly. I've been on a date with a girl and she complained that men never say anything, then I said we can't, first move has to be from girl.", "When you pay to upgrade and it run out. I have found that when you get likes the system doesn't match you with them. I wants you to upgrade. They then timed out and their gone. Don't pay for the upgrade or you'll just have to delete your account like I did. It should be above all, about finding a connection.", 'Having a limit on likes per day isn\'t a bad idea, but this app\'s limit is almost cartoonish. I can\'t spend more than a few minutes per 24 hours swiping without being told I need to pay 3 WHOLE DOLLARS to keep going. It\'s asinine. On top of that, almost everything else is locked behind paywalls. Though I do like that you can list your pronouns without having to first pick "man or woman." But that\'s just basic decency, not a feature', "I've been on Bumble for a few weeks now. Ended up paying for the boost, matched with someone who, for their prompt, asked me to verify my photo. Prior to this I had tried probably 20 times to verify, and was never able to. Yes I tried photos with just myself. Mimicking the pose, hand gestures, and even location exactly, but couldn't verify. Now I'm stuck on the verification screen, I'm being ignored by the support team. 0/5", "To the pros: fairly clean & simple UI, tho a bit outdated. Cons: gps based search, meaning swiping endlessly tons of people in proximity, including tourists & people in the airport and there's no way to filter out. And you have to scroll all way down to find out person is living somewhere else or doesn't disclose. So looks like tinder at this point and more oriented towards finding one night stand nearby. Exhausting & very disappointing experience for me and after a long time trying it, I'm out", "Even after having premium it doesn't let's text to someone who liked my profile. It clearly showed in best bees match. But it didn't let me text. What a pathetic app. They just want you to keep browsing and keep paying for super swipes or compliments even after buying premium. You will get nothing here. I think they just got some profiles when they launched the app. Might be no longer active because this app doesn't let people text even after liking from both sides.", "Bamble has completely changed my dating game! The interface is so user-friendly and the profiles are detailed. I've had some great conversations and even met up with a few matches. The safety features make me feel comfortable putting myself out there ..", 'Sent a support message because the app was malfunctioning and did not hear back. Super frustrating as it\'s deleted messages, not notified me about matches, and given me at least 20 "ghost matches." Meaning that it tells me that I have \'seconds left to reapond\' and never see a match or any reference to one when I log in. 8/18 Update: Messaged the support team on FB yesterday like the moderator suggested and haven\'t heard back.....', "The app generally is easy to navigate. But it works on Likes. If a person likes another person, that other person will not see the profile of whom has 'Liked them, unless they subscribe. I tried with and without subscription, if you don't pay you don't see the 'Liker'. I think there is misunderstanding of this being like Facebook and folk randomly 'like' . Bumble needs the 'how long since been active' or filter out the 'non-users' somehow. The speed dating is awful 😖 Get rid or show a pic.", "The facial recognition and it's term in this app is sucks!! My profile pics is exactly as my now i take, but still wrong! Why not verify person in manually like the other app dating? AI mostly can be wrong! And the face fiture of people can change as the time always change. Hope this app can use other method to verified person!!", "So I decided to buy a week of premium. It's not worth the $20. Once it's gone you just get people that don't match your filters. Having to pay to filter people based on important things like having or wanting kids in the first place is pretty sleezy. They also take away any spotlights you have left over when premium expires. The distance filter doesn't look at where people live, and is terrible for people looking for long-term. Prepare to either pay too much for Bumble or be disappointed.", "My biggest complaint is there's no swipe priority to people who superswiped. It'll give me a notification that I got superswiped but it'll take me days to find out who actually did it. I would greatly appreciate if you could fix that as pretty much every other app places priority on that stuff and not having it makes superswipes seem kinda useless.", 'Would never recommend, because of 0 support. Wrote 5 times - no response. Bought a lifetime Premium. Had to simply reinstall the app, and now the premium purchase is gone, verifying is not possible (just shows "Oops" on their website). Have sent various requests, almost a week past - no answer. Waste of money.', "Terrible. I tried the BFF part and every woman I matched with is terrible at communicating. It doesn't seem like anyone is serious about making friends even though their profile says it. They all take over 1-2 days to reply or not at all and they even messaged me first. I ask open ended questions too. It seems people are just looking for validation by matching. If you're looking for genuine friendships, this ain't it. These people are fake and some are just looking for IG followers.", "Don't buy the spot lights!!!! The app will self activate them and email support stopped trying to help! I tried just not being on for a couple days till subscription weekly one was added when I did log on it has already used it and times out! Yes I emailed them and they tried a couple time but stopped helping. Lost 5 so far. And they are not doing anything to help. Very disappointed in you guys. I'm done I've cancelled the subscription and not trying to get your help when you just blow it off.", "I would like to love this app, but it is actively keeping matches apart. I purchased the unlimited likes package and swiped through everyone in my area, yet it still says there are people that like me nearby even though I can not swipe on anyone else. It's just trying to make me but the ability to see my likes. They don't care about people getting into relationships they just care about money. If you do get this app, don't spend any money on it because it's only worth the free content", 'I tried several times to get my picture verified, including taking a picture, posting it, and then without moving, taking the same picture in the verify area. They still said I could not be verified. I contacted customer service about it, and my app got stuck on the verify photo page and would not leave that page. I then contacted customer service two more times about it and still stuck. It would be nice to at least be able to try the app out.', "Well developed but core functionality is behind a paywall, and there's no incentive to pay for an app that feels dead. Honestly it looks great but actually seeing who has matched you is behind a pricy paywall, so it's a dice roll as to whether two people see each other, and this makes the limited ability to like people (an otherwise good feature) greatly lower the ceiling on chances of matching. People have moved onto other apps."]

title: Sago Mini Dogs
description:
*Try before you buy!* Play Dogs free 6 times, no strings attached.

Get ready for a puppy playdate! There’s so much to do with your new best friends. 

PICK A PUP AND START PLAYING!   
Meet five canine companions that are ready to play – there’s Akira, Stella, Rex, Molly, and Harvey, too! Find each dog in their own unique setting, like a city park, a farm, the beach, or the desert. Next, pick an activity to do with your puppy pal!

TAKE CARE OF YOUR FURRY FRIENDS 
Is your pup feeling peckish? Give them some snacks and see which treat is their favorite! Get them squeaky clean with a nice bubble bath before heading over to the grooming station to brush, style, and trim their fur. Ready to give your pooch a brand new look? Play dress-up with tons of fun accessories and make your pup look their best! Next, have a dog-friendly dance party and make some music together. 
 
NURTURING PLAY THAT BUILDS EMPATHY
When little ones care for a pet, they develop social-emotional skills like empathy and responsibility. In Sago Mini Dogs, kiddos respond to their pup’s emotions which helps them learn compassion through nurturing play. 

• Play with five different dogs – Akira, Stella, Rex, Molly, and Harvey
• Interact with your pup in five mini-games
• Get creative with different ways to style and customize your furry friend
• Imaginative, open-ended activities that encourage pretend play
• Perfect for preschoolers, ages 2-5
• Play without WiFi or internet – great for travel

Privacy Policy

Sago Mini is committed to protecting your privacy and the privacy of your children. We adhere to the strict guidelines set forth by COPPA (Children’s Online Privacy Protection Rule), which ensure the protection of your child’s information online. Read our full privacy policy here.

Terms of use: sagomini.link/termsofuse

Sago Mini is an award-winning company devoted to play. We make apps and toys for preschoolers worldwide. Toys that seed imagination and grow wonder. We bring thoughtful design to life. For kids. For parents. For giggles. 

We love making new friends!
Instagram: @sagomini
Facebook: Sago Mini
Say hello@sagomini.com

title: Dog Training App — GoDog
description:
POSITIVE-BASED DOG TRAINING. BUILT-IN DOG CLICKER. TRAIN YOUR DOG ANYTIME, ANYWHERE!

Are you a happy dog owner? Do you want to know how to train your dog in easy-to-follow steps? Download GoDog — smart guide for dog training and taking good care of your pet.

Here you will find a full lesson’s pack with step-by-step video instructions verified by professional dog trainers, built-in dog whistle and clicker, health and care diary, time walking schedule, useful articles, and other features that help your dog stay healthy and happy!

DOG TRAINER APP
These are easy-to-grasp and reproduce lessons for your dog that assist you with essential behavioral training. Teach your puppy to be socialized and well-adjusted without overpaying for dog trainer’s services. All lessons are made together with highly qualified dog trainers. 

You will find different lesson packages, such as Basic (sit, down, stay, no, paw), Good Pup Behavior (come, stop barking, chewing, don’t jump), Puppy Training Course (potty, collar, come on leash), Dog Tricks and Games, etc. We offer basic lessons for free.

HEALTH DIARY FOR KEEPING YOUR FURRY FRIEND FIT
With the GoDog Health & Care Diary, you'll never forget to take care of your pet. Create reminders for vaccinations, medications, visits to the vet, and other important events in your dog's life and save a history of these events. Track the hygiene care of your doggy including bathing, teeth brushing, nail clipping, ear cleaning, etc. Define dog schedule and let the GoDog app remind you when the next action is due.

WHISTLE AND CLICKER FOR TRAINING DOGS
Use these features to improve and strengthen the results of your dog training exercises. Dog clicker training is gaining popularity for its ease of use and positive effect. Download GoDog and use our built-in dog clicker with 3 different sounds!

WALKING TRACKER
Keep an eye on how much exercise your dog gets on a daily basis. It will help you adjust your walking routine to your dog’s specific needs.

DOG HEALTH ARTICLES
It’s extremely important to read up-to-date and verified information so as not to harm the dog. All information and articles in GoDog are checked by professional canine experts and vets, so you can have a rest, while learning something new about your fluffy friend.

Download the GoDog app now and start dog training and spending quality time with your four-legged friend!

Please feel free to contact us: info@godog.me
Privacy Policy: https://www.godog.me/privacy-policy

Uninstalled", 'I love this app, I used to have my dog around the house smelling because I have ADHD and I forget sometimes but the reminder feature on this app really got me going. I love that you can teach your dog tricks and the app shows you how to gain trust with a dog, but overall this app is very great I recommend.', "Wow it's really working! My dog just learned how to sit in just a single minute! 🤩", 'Easy to use & understand. Contains the information I need', 'Amazing app,the guides help me to train my Rottweiler mix and it gives me an idea of what I should and should not do when training my dog.', "Honestly, amazing app, but a bit expensive for a phone app. Especially when it's subscription based. It's a training app, so technically once the dog learns the tricks, there's not added value from the app (no one pays to read articles that are free online) so a one time payment would've been reasonable, but I'm not payons 55 dollars a year to track walks! Too bad cause I would've loved to use it.", "The app works fine and does as intended, but to learn any of the good tricks you have to pay monthly or yearly. My dogs know all but one of the tricks that are unlocked. I got this so they could learn some more complicated tricks like roll over or sit pretty, not sit, stay, or paw. This app showed one good thing. One of my dogs learned paw. Please make it so I can learn the hard ones without paying. title: My Smart Dog: Virtual Puppy
description:
There are some smart puppies. Do you want to adopt them? They are waiting for you. In this game, you can own your beautiful house with a big garden and live with your puppies. In your big garden, you can walk and play with them. Maybe you can find something super cool! Smart puppies like to hide things to give you a nice surprise. Do you wanna it? Come on and let fun begin!

Help:
🦴  Interact and play with your puppies.
🦴  Feed puppies and enjoy your happy time.
🦴  Go outsides to play with your puppies.
🦴  If puppies are tired, let them have a good rest.

Features:
🍗  Unique painting styles and wonderful pictures
🍗  Rich backgrounds and massive props
🍗  Different mini games and ways of interactions
🍗  Exclusive adorable cute puppies 

They can’t wait to meet you. Don’t miss it! Download and play with them!
summary: The funnest puppy feeding game. Have fun with smart puppies!

title: TikTok
description:
Ang TikTok ay isang social-platform ng maikling video na pinaaandar ng musika. Maging sayaw man ito, malayang estilo o pagganap, hinihikayat ang mga tagalikha na hayaan ang kanilang imahinasyon na mamayagpag at maging malaya sa paghayag. Dahil idinisenyo ito para sa bagong henerasyon ng tagalikha, nagbibigay-daan ang TikTok sa mga gumagamit para mabilis at madaling makalikha ng mga natatanging maikling video para ibahagi sa mga kaibigan at sa mundo. TikTok ang bagong kultural na pamantayan para sa mga bagong tagalikha. Nagsisikap kaming pahusayin pa ang malikhaing pag-iisip na maging bahagi ng content revolution.

[Pagkilala ng mukha]
Mabilis na pagkuha ng larawan at perpektong pangmukhang tampok na tumutugma sa lahat ng iyong maganda, astig, wacky, kengkoy at nakapangingilabot na ekspresyon.

[Magandang Kalidad]
Mabilis na mag-load, maayos ang interface, at walang lag. 
Ang bawat detalye ay ipinapakita sa perpektong kalidad. 

[Mobile na Studio]
Ang perpektong pagsasama ng artipisyal na katalinuhan at pagkuha ng larawan. 
Pagpapahusay ng produkto sa pamamagitan ng sinkronisasyon ng ritmo, mga espesyal na effect at advanced na teknolohiya. 
Gawin ang iyong telepono na isang ganap na malikhaing studio.

[Malawak na Librarya ng Musika]
Dalhin ang malikhain mong potensyal sa susunod na antas at buksan ang mundo ng walang katapusang posibilidad.

comments: ["It's great, the experience and all. The ads is bearable. However, it was my first time experiencing the app glitch, and it's 𝘳𝘦𝘢𝘭𝘭𝘺 bad. When I posted new videos it suddenly disappeared. Checked my gallery and it's saved there, tried and posted again but still the same, updated, cleared cache, re-opened STILL the same. Fam, please fix this.", "The app is great, it's fun, very easy to use, and the community is nice. Although the only problem is whenever you search or looking for something, the only videos that pop up is the videos from your country only. User's cannot see the videos from other country and this is frustrating. I suggest that the app should include an option to choose which countries video to see to keep people entertained.", "The update is very nice. Lots of new and better features, but there are 2 reasons why I don't like the update. First is that the add to favorites button is gone for videos. And second, is that the text-to-speech voice can't be changed anymore. I miss the old TikTok from 2020 cause it still had the features that everyone liked. Some people have been commenting on my videos for tutorials on how to solve these problems. Please fix these.", "Not much of a problem but I'm giving this a 2 star because the app doesn't let me download any videos and pictures! sometimes it does but when I open the photos/gallery and click on the video I downloaded only a black screen appears and a note pops out and says “Can't play video” And it doesn't let me change profile picture!! When I click save it says “retry”.", 'It was a great app at first,but now it\'s becoming boring. First. when I\'m gonna edit photos into a slideshow, the "switch to photo mode" or whatever it\'s called isn\'t there. Second. Remove the bots that always have a link on their profile. Please fix this so I can rate 5 stars. Thank you!', "I change my review from 5 to 3, why? I encounter so many bugs and errors one time, i “accidentally” click the shop (tiktok shop) after a few minutes the app keeps crashing, the way i swipe a video wasn't so... Smooth. The only way to fix it (it didn't even stop when i 'clear cache' it) is to erase all your data/clear data, and i am confused that, why only 'iphone' had a dark mode thingy, why isn't not on android? We/us badly want it, but i guees it is only on iOS devices, hoping you will fix it!", 'its a great app. so much to discover, trends, educational videos. its basically the best social app for teenagers and adults to have fun with and make videos. but i have some issues with it. throughout my experience it has been great but if i click the tiktok yellow basket to view an item that got my interest it takes a while to load. and sometimes the picture of the product does not show up. and 2nd issue is that when i make a video everything seems great until my Story/Photo mode disappeared.', 'it would be nice if tiktok had this feature where in collections, it would have a drop down menu titled "sort by" and have different options to choose from. i\'m also not a fan about how when i remove a deleted video from a collection, it refreshes to the beginning, it can become frustrating especially if you\'re trying to delete through 1000s of favourited videos. overall, this app has been super neat, thank you!', "I love the app, I truly do. I have followers and friends on TikTok and it is genuinely an amazing app. The reason I rated it 4 stars was because of the many errors I have when making videos. One of them is that I can't add pictures to Scroll and it scrolls by itself automatically. The button to change from video (auto swipe) and pictures is completely gone for me. My account is mainly for uploading photos on it and I won't be able to function without it. Please fix this!!", "I gave it a two, tho the contents are fun (if u don't get on the wrong side) it's sometimes repetitive. Like I've seen the tiktok alr for like a month ago then it shows up again which is annoying, and the slideshow one when I click it, can't it just be the same as before wherein you can pause the video w/out ending up in that thingy?", 'The app in shape is good enough but, there\'s some minor issues. The first one, when I click the "not interested" of course, it works. But, the content preferences doesn\'t change at all. It\'s still there, and it\'s rather annoying. The second one, I suggest making the "content preferences/filtered words" a much higher number then 100(ex: 200) because, some people including myself would want to remove some hashtags that result in various kinds of contents. But, the app is great overall from that.', "Since the last update where there's ads. The sound of the ads overlaps with the original video. Whether I skip it or not, it will overlap, and I have no choice but to close the app or forced stop the app since the sounds are still playing even after closing the app. This app was a great before the Ads. Stop putting ads in the video its bad enough that there are ads in between or every other scroll. 🙄", "The app is very entertaining, there's a lot of genres in every situation you are right now. But the problem is when I tap the app to use it the video is so slow to pop up, just like the other users problem, the sound some times were getting faster than the video or slower - in short, the music cannot cope up with the video; plus the video lagging every time. Fix all the problems we have in your application TikTok.", 'It was a great app at first,but now it\'s becoming boring. First. when I\'m gonna edit photos into a slideshow, the "switch to photo mode" or whatever it\'s called isn\'t there. Second. Remove the bots that always have a link on their profile. Please fix this so I can rate 5 stars. Thank you!', "Every update something change yes but it does too with the bugs. I don't understand why everytime just recently tho everytime I record a video or content especially when it's a transition or lipsync it always hang in the middle or before the end of the video which really pissed me off. Please try to do something about this one especially TikTok is one of my go to application whenever I'm bored or something. Thanks!", "Needs improvement for zflip devices. It's a lot laggy than usual, and it force closes, making me start from square one with my edits. It got so frustrating lately that i seldom use it anymore for my edits. I use third-party apps now. They also need to filter out fake accounts. My account got copied more than i can think of. They should create more safety updates for Creators.", "Its a good app. However even though I click on the 'not intrested button' the same trend keeps popping up of my for you page. Even though my preferred language is english, korean videos keep poping up and there is no english videos on my for you page. And whenever I watch tiktok the app lags a lot. I hope you can fix the problems im experiencing.", 'I like the videos and photos shown in "for you" page, And then now when I open the app it crashes. I reported it and had done what they said. But the app still crashes. I like the app but I can\'t open in now because it just keeps crashing. I hope the crash gets fixed.', "It's a great app! I started using this app about a year ago, and it has changed so well! There are so many things you can do with this app .. chat with your friends, make videos, get famous you can also watch drills/exercises to get rid of boredom that's all I do 24/7! It's also very addictive and every time I see a new move and exercise I check it out as fast as I can and practice and practice you can add it to my favorites if I want to rewatch it again and again", "Since you guys make an ads pop up between video scrollin or in mid video that i watch. IT SUCK!!! Bc the sound of the ads won't come off even after the ads video finish, so its stuck in the video that i watch. I watch the tik tok video and listening to the sound of the video and the sound of the previous ads that i watched. Some of my friends said that they also have the same problem. Please fix it!!!", "It's okay, but whenever there's an update the app wouldn't open and it's frustrating because everytime I have to delete the app from my phone. my drafts would be lost if I uninstalled it then downloaded it back again.", 'Very nice,,stress reliever,,it helps develop your self-esteem,,,artistic app,,very challenging and you can learn a lot of things,,you meet a lot of people from different cultures and you can reach out with family and friends and also can create good friendships even if it is from other countries and you are updated about what is viral and useful for us...', 'It is great app , it\'s alot of fun, there\'s all different types of humor in this app, it is entertaining and helpful, but my issue is that when I try to make a slideshow post, the "switch to photo mode" option is gone and I can\'t make any slideshows anymore please bring this option back it was alot of fun.', "After the ads started showing up, the audio from the ad will remain and overlap with the normal videos. It still continues to play even after closing the app. I have to force stop the app from settings to stop the audio from playing. It's been happenning so much that I will uninstall the app instead. Not worth the hassle. I can still watch the same videos from Facebook anyway", "I've been using this app for maybe 2/3 years (different devices) and nothing wrong happened in those years, but lately after the new update,I can't search videos! I can only search for users,sounds,hashtags,lives and shops. I have been reinstalling and clearing cache for maybe millions of times and get the problem fixed but it was just temporary. It's really struggling me and other people that have this problem,please please pleaseee fix this problem!!! 😭", 'amazing app, but whenever i post a video i edited on capcut, the quality always sucks. please bring the “allow high-quality uploads” feature back on android! i had this feature on my android phone a year ago, and when i updated tiktok, it was gone. please bring this feature back on android, it would really help a lot of editors who edit on an android phone.', 'It was a wondeful app, but then it starts to get boring when i click the photos and there\'s no other option like "video" or "photo" we want the swipe photo things back, and all au writer\'s are struggling bc of this suation. Please fix it, thankyousomuch!! I will rate 5 star if u can fix it. Thankyousomuch again!!', "The peak of entertainment. However, I'd like to suggest a feature for the app. I suggest that we could have an option to remove the live tiktoks that randomly appears on the fyp. And Also a live button for those who WANTS to watch live tiktoks. Thanks", "Idk what happened but I can't see the filters used by a creator when I'm scrolling, so I have to click on the music that they used and find their vids so that I can use the filter. I already updated the app and rebooted my phone but it doesn't do anything. So FIX YOUR APP.", 'before this i using this app just for fun but now its so many educational , tips and cooking video or more about knowledge here. The improvement very up to date day by day. Make user more comfortable. But please improve the playlist we made on "Favourites". Developer have to improve which is , user can rename the playlist , can choose the date add make it the old to new , new to old. title: My Puppy Friend - Cute Pet Dog
description:
If you are a pet lover, these cute puppies would definitely melt your heart!

Your love and care could make the little ones' life different! Take them home and feed them with delicious food. Or give them a shower to wash off the dirt. A stylish makeup pairing with a chic outfit will help the pets stand out in the show, which would award you with a lot of decorations and take the puppies' home up a notch! Parkour, seek out the bones…many fun activities are ready to blow your mind!

Features:
- 6 cute puppies that melt your heart
Life gets a whole lot more interesting if you take these little cuties home. 
- Collet loving hearts to open the Show where you may get decorations
Each time you complete a mini game, one heart would be awarded to you. With 3 hearts, you can join the Show and win the decorations.
- Earn coins and exchange them for nice items
Take the challenges with your pets to earn as many coins as you can and exchange them for food, outfits and other nice things.
- Fun-filled mini games work well with the amazing scenes
Have fun with your doggies in such gorgeous scenes and wonderful activities.

About Libii Game:
With over 600 million downloads and growing, Libii is committed to creating innovative games for kids. We'll keep working on establishing a good relationship with both parents and their children and bringing a healthy, happy atmosphere for them.
Visit us: http://www.libii.com/
Like us: http://www.facebook.com/LibiiGame
Contact us: Got any ideas? Suggestions? Need technical support? Please feel free to contact us 24/7 at WeCare@libii.com

Need You Know:
This app is totally free to download and play, some basic items are also free to use, but some additional items need you to purchase and pay to unlock. Therefore, if you do not want to use these items, please turn off the in-app purchase in your settings. Thanks.
