title: Fancy Dogs - Puppy Care Game
description:
Dogs have never been this fancy before. Join us on our fun journey of collecting cute puppies and turning them into the fanciest dogs ever seen in this new free cute dogs game in the history.

Play addictive match 3 puzzles to collect cute puppies and costumes. Can you find all dog breeds and costume sets? Dress up your fancy dogs and show them off to your friends and family. Go find out more about the secret life of pups.

Features:

- Another fun adventure created by the minds behind Fancy Cats, suitable for any dog lover out there, from boys to girls, from young to old.

- Prepare for the ultimate cuteness, with a huge selection of fancy dogs: 20+ different dog breeds with distinctive personalities. Collect them all: fabulous Chihuahuas, adorable French Bulldogs, gentle Dalmatians, and many more such as the Beagle, Rottweiler, Pitbull, Chow Chow, Staffordshire Bull Terrier... We are missing your favorite dog breed? Don’t worry! We plan on adding many more in the future such as the Bichon Frise, Labrador Retriever, Great dane, Cocker Spaniel, Shih Tzu, Pomeranian, Doberman Pinscher and of course the Pug.

- Watch as your pups play and talk to not only each other but also to you. Wake them up as they are sleeping and feed them with treats. Name each of your new pet with adorable names such as Molly, Bailey, Daisy, Max, Fluffy, and Bella; and start bonding with them as soon as possible.

- Pet your little puppies and see their reaction. Each puppy will have their own reaction.

-  What is a pet without a toy? A huge selection of toys for your fancy dogs to play with. Watch your puppies make funny faces as you give them different toys. Have your cute dogs chase a robot squirrel. Or give them a giant donut to eat. Can you guess what happens?

- Raise and take care of the fancy dogs from cute little puppies to full blown grown-ups. Each pup just can't grow up fast enough.

- Spoil the cute dogs with a huge collection of costumes. Let your fancy puppies become firefighter, wizards, police officers, etc. The possibilities are endless.

- 300+ different addicting match 3 puzzles, with a wide variety of difficulty for you to either relax with or challenge yourself. The more challenging, the bigger the prizes. Each match 3 puzzle was designed with different fun mechanics in mind. Each puzzle rewards you with a star, which you can use to open chests containing new prices.

- 9+ dog parks with beautiful backgrounds, which you can even upgrade to make them even fancier.

- Take pictures of your pups and share them on social media to show off how stylish you can make your pups.

- Show off your puppies with other players, and make some new friends along the way. Can you make your pups be the cutest of them all? 

- Come back every day for your free reward.

- One of the best girls games / mom games / puppy games free for dog lovers.

- The game is entirely free, containing in-app purchases. Aphmau fans will love this for sure!
summary: Collect 20+ different dog breeds with distinctive personalities.

title: with My DOG
description: ▼▼Life Changes, but Friendship Never Changes▼▼ Attention: dog lovers and animal lovers, Spend more time with your puppies and get to know them. Various kinds and personalities. Let's start a new life with unique puppies. ▼Dogs in this game ▼ Shiba Inu, Toy Poodle, Chihuahua, Labrador Retriever and German Shepherd. More than 190 kinds of dogs with different fur colors and patterns. ▼Meet new dogs at Friends Plaza ▼ Find the dog of destiny. Spend your time with the special one? or try to see how many dogs you can meet? Utilize Friends Hotel and Foster Parents as well. ▼Keep a dog on your smartphone ▼ Interact with your puppy anytime, anywhere. Your puppy show you the tricks by recognizing your voice. The outside sceneries will change according to the time you actually spend. Take AR photos/videos of your dogs in your room or outside, and post them on SNS with #withmydog ▼Your own family ▼ Costumes, hats, glasses and more. Unique items over 600 kinds. Give your puppy a stencil mark to make them special. Dog's room interior-decoration can also be customized. Free-to-play, a dog simulation game. Let's start a new life with a puppy. ▼▼About Neilo▼▼ ▼Follow us on: Twitter　@Neilo_JP Instagram　@withmy_friends_neilo ▼Official HP: https://withmydog.neilo.co.jp/en/
summary: Pet your puppies, play together with toys, go for a walk together and more!

comments: ['Wanted to get "Little Friends" for the switch, found this which is actually done by the same people. Not disappointed at all, still has the origins of Nintendogs which I have missed. Need to add the ability to Bath your dog and give them treats though! Overall cute larl game, definitely wanting it on the switch too.', "As this is a newer kind of version of Nintendogs, I don't understand the point. You must pay for your own dog if it isn't a German Shepherd, and you can't change the fur color unless you pay to do so. May I add, you can't be under the age of twelve to make purchases. It wasn't my childhood, (I'm a Gen Z,) but I'm pretty sure the entire premise of Nintendogs was to choose your own pooch to make fun memories with.", 'This game is amazing!!!! 5 stars. Maybe in the future we can give our dogs a bath, treats and have a few more rooms, but otherwise this game is amazing!! Definitely the best dog care game. Cute graphics, clothes and furniture. I give this game 5 stars and hope everyone gives it a try. I absolutely love this game and recommend it to anyone looking for a nice dog game. Hopefully there will be lots of cool updates!!! Great work on this amazing game!!!', "Some Reasons I Gave This Game a 3 : 1. You cannot have play with a bunch of dogs in the same room only just one.. 2. Lots of the things in the shop are very expensive in my opinion... 3. It's also unfair for me because only the German Shepherd and the Toy Poodle are free but some of their colour tones you can have with Real Money... Soooooo those are my reasons, I know that they're a bit arrogant and shows the game's flaws but I think it's better to be honest even if the truth hurts!", "This game is forcing, I can hardly do what I want and at the start it says 'choose your first pet' or something along the lines, and you literally only have the option of a boring blonde thing. You get to choose the colours as black and white but you still end up with a boring blonde thing. Disappointing really.", 'I have the cat version too and absolutely adore both games. The creators anf developers really did a wonderful job. Iv looked for years and years for a Nintendogs type game and am so happy its finally here. Thankyou so much guys. Please can you add more dog breeds one day. This game is 10/10', "The graphics are good but everything else is a bust. Money money money. All this game cares about. You have to pay REAL MONEY just for your dog to learn ONE TRICK!! Like come on not cool. And in the begging it says to pick your dog, but it doesnt even let ME choose the dog. If I could give 0 stars, i would. But I can't. Heart broken this game is a pay to play thought I found a good game.", "This is an amazing game with lots of features!!!! I think towards the future this game could have maybe a few more dog breeds as well as more rooms, a bath feature, being able to give your dog a treat and maybe more personalitys for the puppys!!!!!! Other than that this it deserves 5 stars in my opinion and it's a great quality dog game simulation!! :D", 'I almost never leave low reviews. If I dislike a game I just move on. However, anyone thinking of playing this game should know that you will install the game, be forced to wait for another 400mb installation once you load the game, enter your birthdate, and then after all that the game randomly selects which pet you need to spend your time with. The others are locked behind a paywall. Isnt the point of the game to offer power of choice with a pet that fits your likes? I mean... just no.', "It's such a cute game, pretty similar to nintendogs. But that's why I love it! But i wish you you guys could add bubble baths for the dogs, bc it's more fun to wash them then brush. I also kinda want you guys to add treats, when a dog behaves u can give it a treat or when it does tricks :D", "Perfect for kids and nostalgic adults who grew up with Nintendogs. Has the most fair monetization I've seen in a free game (few ads. No cryptocurrency, prices are in dollars. Things like tricks that are paywalled are not necessary to enjoy gameplay, and prices are cheap) so parents can feel safe letting their kids play. Gameplay is Nintendogs lite. Not a lot of content, but very good at scratching that itch for a loving pet. First dog is random, but you can reset app until you get one you like", 'This is a good game, graphics are good, dogs are adorable, my one suggestion is that you add more dogs like Pomeranian, Great Dane, husky, but overall this game is fantastic 😊', 'Can you add more things to do? title: Pet Rescue Saga
description:
Puppies and kittens are stuck between the puzzle blocks in this Pet Rescue Saga adventure and need your help! Hurry and save them from the evil Pet Snatchers! 

Match 2 or more blocks of the same color to clear the levels and save the pets. Matching moves are limited so plan carefully to blast as many blocks as possible, solve the puzzles, and save the pets. Your puzzle skills will be tested with hours of block busting fun!

Join the rescue mission and solve increasingly challenging match 3 puzzles! Match and blast blocks in a variety of events and puzzles to discover a whole new variety of pets waiting to be rescued! Not only do you save the puppies and kittens but you also build an animal shelter for them. Blast your way through the puzzle levels!

Lots of fun events
Blast blocks and solve new matching puzzles to win boosters and bonus rewards! Discover fun time-limited games and play increasingly challenging levels, so blast the right blocks!

Petopia: a whole city, but for pets!
Don’t leave your animals out in the cold, send them off to Petopia City! Clear puzzles to build a city for your rescued pets and visit them in their new home.

Grow your pet
Every 2 weeks, collect red blocks within the game levels to grow your pet by earning treats; the more red blocks, the more treats!

Weekly match 3 quests
Complete match 3 quests every week and gain rewards by solving new puzzles. Hop on to the next quest and start matching blocks!

With 5,600+ pet puzzles and more levels added every 2 weeks to the game, Pet Rescue Saga is a real match 3 blast! Are you ready for some pet-tastic fun?

Pet Rescue Saga from the makers of Candy Crush Saga, Farm Heroes Saga, and Bubble Witch 3 Saga is free to play but some in-game items such as extra moves or lives will require payment. You can turn off the payment feature by disabling in-app purchases in your device’s settings.

By downloading Pet Rescue Saga you agree to our terms of service which can be found at https://king.com/termsAndConditions

Do not sell my data: King shares your personal information with advertising partners to personalize ads. Learn more at https://king.com/privacyPolicy. If you wish to exercise your Do Not Sell My Data rights, you can do so by contacting us via the in-game help center or by going to https://soporto.king.com/contact

comments: ['I really like this game. Plenty of gifts. Some levels are very hard but you can ask for help from others and after playing the round for a while you can accumulate extra moves. I like the fact that it takes 5 minutes to get more lives unlike some games that take 30min. I changed my rating to 4 stars and even considering 3 stars because the adds are very long and repetitive. Most adds are 30 sec and the game looses its interest. The worst part is, you have to look at adds that you already have.', "On mobile app, android phone. Level 930, you can not get past. Went to Kings community forums, same issue with people in there, there is no fix, app is updated, not connected through FB or anything. Developer please fix problem. Many are saying in the forum what is wrong as well. About to delete bc I won't connect it to my FB account or anything else. Just want to play like I have been.", 'This game app is really a cheat. It claims that the internet is not available when I certainly have it. So many missed rewards with this ploy; a crafty way to try and force players to buy boosts for the game. Now the game offers extra moves if an ad is watched...surprise! Tap on the watch ad choice and the game completely shuts down makibg you start the same level again! No way to address this problem and it has been going on for weeks. Where is customer service to correct this issue?', "I like older UI version better than this update version of UI. I like how older UI version where each level is on a pathway of a different world from our real world. Gives us players a feeling that were exploring pet's world with realistic graphic landscape of what would look like for animals without humans. But we get this new UI with cheap and laziness 3d graphic design of this game. The game has lost a lot of feelings and excitements about this game.", "I play this game everyday and really like it, the problem I've had for the past week or so is that as soon as the game comes on for me to play it cuts off and goes back to my home page!! Not allowing me to even play the game!!! The game is updated do I need to know how do I fix this so I can continue to play?? Don't want to uninstall it but if I can't play it then why have it 😓 Please help.....", "I can't play beyond 6268 why.what is the problem ?can you guys fix it for me. I can't also update it and hell no I am not Uninstalling n installing to loose my level .If I do then I am no longer going to play any king games like I have stop doing to the others. Kindly fix my problem now I want to play new levels. I'm tired stacked at random levels. I want to play beyond 6522 Remove all my blockage please .remove all blocks it's getting boring every time.remove al blockages", "Pet rescue is a lot of fun until you reach a puzzle you can't win that you've played for days using power ups even the power ball and still no win? You want to quit deleting and maybe find something new that's boring", 'Kinda of challenging I am kinda struck on level 27 I am more determine then ever to beat the level. Great game for all ages toddler on up. Give it a try for a while. U will love it!', 'Why did it get rid of the mountain level. I looked forward to that every time. You could win so much stuff play it. Getting rid of it ruined this game for me..', 'Great game. The only thing that I do not understand is that the city is only on spring. I recomend making the place perminent and add new gimmicks and buildings.', 'Everything was fine. On level 1082 or something like that. Got a new phone and it put me back to level one!!!! This used to be my favorite game. Debating on deleting!!!', "Fun for awhile but you end up having to spend a lot of money to advance once you reach the higher levele. I'm finally saying no after wasting too much $. Uninstalled", 'I have been playing this game since a long time . I was somewhere above 4000+game I have lost the count. I would be somewhere near. Wrote this many time to avail my lost game but damn n poor rating if my game isint coming back.', '📢Game is not what it used to be(played this game for years). There is way too many tricks and gimmicks to get you to spend money. I will be uninstalling ‼️', "Game used to be fun now it just keeps you stuck on really ridiculous boards for far too long! Seriously considering deleting. And I'm on level 5976!", "The levels get too hard too fast. Plus, the blocks or pets don't always fall the same way even if you make an identical move both times. I liked it alright at first but now it's just a waste of time. Uninstalling.", "Have been playing this forever but every time they put the city up you touch the next level. It goes black in your app shuts off. It's like they're in a rush to change stuff. I like change. I like the extra perks but make sure it works", "Why do you have to join a team in order to play the damn game?! Stupid! Uninstalling! 05/03/23 I'm on level 5361 and I clearly was winning the game early on and there's no possible way I could've lost the game! That's crazy! I only had to collect 6 yellow balls, I got 3 had lots of moves left, then i got another and all of a sudden, the yellow balls stopped dropping..... how convenient. Smh...", "Love love the game. Just update the game, and it toke my coins 🪙 and I'm stuck on a super hard level. Maybe I shouldn't have updated 😕 🤔 and I game 5stars🤔🤔😔😔", 'I love playing this game but ever since the latest update it will not load... but on the occasion that it does load when you pass a level that goes to the next level it freezes. When you restart the game you lose all of the data or the accomplishment that you just did. I had over 30 days of consecutive logons and lost all of it. Please fix this issue.', 'USED TO LOVE THIS GAME... LEVEL 3500+ recent issues with Petopia challenges... I have contacted them multiple times...completing all of their requests to fix the issues... only to be condescending to with more ridiculous requests that would warn me of losing reward items that I have earned by possibly spending a ridiculous amount of REAL MONEY to play this game... CUSTOMER SERVICE IS A DYING BREED... PLEASE COMMENT IF YOU AGREE!!!!! UPDATE...NOW THEY WANT A VIDEO OF WHAT IS SCREWED UP!!!', "I was up to 2204 and lost everything and it wants me start at 1484, nah I don't think so. Too hard to start over. But I actually love the game itself", 'I keep getting cheated out of my 7 day award. It keep saying week after week. That I did not play the day before. But I most certainly did.', 'This game is challenging. It allows you to think. There are moments when you may find it frustrating. It also teaches you patients and you must exercise some level of self control. I find it relaxing and look forward to playing the game whenever I find the time.', 'Fun game.. After 5 people attempting level 3147 over a 2 week period we all agree it is rigged to not be able to go any further .', "Annoyed, earned 50 gold bars and it told me I'd already claimed them on another device at the moment of winning. Never got them. Usually love this game but watched loads of ads to earn the gold bars. Increasing ads have been frustrating for a while but this irritated me beyond all", 'I like the game but I can not buy anything out of the shop. It keeps turning and trying but never connects.', "Love this game but since the recent update keeps freezing and I'm on level 1906 and never experienced this before. No need to buy anything in this game just keep playing till you pass the level! Update:Tried to log in again on a new phone after 3 years of not playing. App freezes every time on login page. Uninstall and re-installed again to no avail. Can't be bothered with it anymore....", 'Cant get into the game to play...go on to it and keeps going back to home screen..please sort or I will delete..game still not working please get it fixed..', "Miss the island & critter carnival. I'm stuck on a level in the regular game, so those are nice diversions!", "If you like spending money to play a game then this one is for you, or if you just wanna play a 10 minute game, cause once you use all your lives you either pay or play another game on your phone, don't count on anyone sending lives either cause they don't , very disappointed in this game , I have a lot of points and they are useless , nowhere do I see how to use them, SUPER HARD LEVELS which there are MANY of are almost impossible to get thru.i really wish they would give more lives to play", "I used to really like this app. When I installed it onto my newest device, it really doesn't want me to go back and replay earlier levels. Then it suddenly made me agree to the new terms of agreement and wiped out all the levels I had done, about 300. This newest version has bouncing arrows continuously prompting me to do what the game wants me to do. I am on level 30 and they are STILL there! Very distracting!", 'I enjoy playing this game, but there are a few things that are pretty irritating. And this is from a player at level 3800+ 1.) I would never buy gold bars. At the end of your lives its easy to accidentally use bars, when you go for a move and hit the buys more lives that pops up. Essentially wasting gold bars. There is no catch. 2.) Harder levels are often impossible to win until the algorithm allows you to win. Game changes allowing you to be able to make moves. No use of actual skill.', 'Still stay stuck on levels way to long. Game would be better if it had ways to get off some of the levels a bit faster. It glitches, For example, you clear most of the blocks, the pets drop down, you have one pet to go, and get the blocks cleared, but the last pet never drops. Or as the level starts, before you make a play at all, it says you have lost the game, uses a life, and there was nothing you could do because the game had no moves to be made when it started. No way to win at times.', "Love the game but there is a problem. Sometimes when you have rescued all the pets it will say too few rescued or not enough moves. The amount rescued at the top is correct but something isn't registering the count right. Very frustrating especially when you use some of your boosters or if you're in the bonus round and it m makes you go back to the first level.", "During the Petopia events the game doesn't let me play any new levels 😒 😤. It seems to take forever to get new boards to begin with then for me not to be able to play just sucks.", "I love this game But I don't like the fact it has repeated stages☹️ I'm currently on 5402 .more like playing the games all over again.", "It has been the worst experience. Even if I buy the boosts, they do not show and even when I don't use them they get disappeared. Super annoying and disheartening.", 'I love this game and have been playing for years, but the 100% of block boards are annoying to say the least. I play other puzzle games and understand the challenge involved, but I play "pet rescue" for the challenge of rescuing pets. Having to clear 100% of the blocks 5 levels in a row misses the whole point and takes the fun out of the concept of the game in my opinion! Again I realize the challenge involved but I think it diminishes the game as a whole.', "This game is fun, and occasionally frustrating. Frustrating in that there are so many pop-up announcements that you need to navigate through just to start playing, and frustrating in that there are some levels where it takes so many attempts to solve them that you're ready to just quit the game forever at some points. But then you get through it and it's addictively fun again! The graphics are cute and it's a great way to while away a commute via transit."]

title: Google Meet
description:
Google Duo has been upgraded to Google Meet. Now you can securely connect, collaborate, and celebrate with the highest-quality video calling, all in one app.

The updated Google Meet app allows you to easily and instantly video call your family and friends or schedule a meeting in advance. Connect with anyone, anywhere across mobile, iOS, Android, web, tablet, and smart devices*.

Features you can look forward to:

Host video calls and meetings, all in one place
Bring everyone who matters most together with group calling or set up your next brainstorm meeting for up to 100 people.

Access on any device
Works across mobile Android, iOS,  tablet, web or smart devices* so everyone can join.

Enjoy high-quality audio and video
Low-light mode and noise cancellation allow everyone to be seen and heard, clearly.

Play with backgrounds and visual effects
Filters, AR masks, effects, family mode and backgrounds make connecting even more fun.

Share content
Present documents, slides, and more during your conference call. Live sharing allows everyone in the meeting to interact with the content being shared, creating a collaborative experience, not just a one-way presentation. You can cowatch YouTube, curate a playlist together, or take turns playing a game.

Follow along
Google speech-to-text technology transcribes your content with real-time captions**, so you won’t miss a detail.

Meet and chat safely
Video meetings are encrypted in transit and our array of safety measures are continuously updated for added protection.

Anyone can join a meeting on Meet via an invitation. However, some capabilities are available only to Google Workspace customers. Learn more about Google Meet:
https://workspace.google.com/products/meet/

Follow us for more:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/googleworkspace
Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/googleworkspace
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/googleworkspace/

*Works on Android TV devices with Android 8.0 or higher. If your Android TV does not have a built-in camera, you will need to connect a USB camera and microphone to your Android TV device.
**Not available in every language.

Data charges may apply. Check your carrier for details.
Specific feature availability may vary based on device specifications.
summary: High quality video calling for Android & iOS phones, tablets, Google Nest & web.

comments: ["I just don't understand why my audio all of a sudden has stopped working after updating google meet. Kindly look into this issue as it's getting frustrating for me to access the meeting facilities properly. I had informed it earlier but no reponse yet received. I have to reboot my system every single time for resolving this technical issues. It's seriously frustrating! Kindly resolve this issue as soon as possible. Thank you.", "Good call quality. Biggest problem is when I call my home devices, it would not give me options to show myself or not. Always makes calls as a video calls. Sometimes I just want phone calls, not a video calls. Another is that u just can't make calls to any number. It has to be a registered number in the Google meet. These two need big improvements. They always make things very complicated w most of their products", "BEWARE! DON'T DOWNLOAD. It came preloaded on my Samsung S2don't want this app! I can't delete it. When I change the auto-uprate feature in the GooglePlay store to off, it automatically changes it back to allow auto-updates. Can't change permissions/unwarranted authority over my phone in settings. Uses data/wifi/storage/battery. Once it's there, you'll never be able to get rid of it. 0 stars if I could.", 'This app was my go-to for video calls for a long time, but the last week or so, it keeps giving me "unexpected error" and "problem starting call". I looked up ways to correct it, which included clearing the cache, clearing app data, and reinstalling the app. It will work for the first call, and then mess up again every single time I do the bug-fixes. Hopefully, there is a way to permanently correct this or some kind of patch update.', "It works really good on full bars for Internet. However, when I get down to 3 bars it glitches then 2 bars it freezes video. Then I loose sound on the last bar. I think it should work better when it shows I do still have Internet at all. Haven't figured out how to send text messages. It hasn't worked for me, yet. Other than that I like MEET. 👍", "I love it. Better than WhatsApp in video quality and audio clarity. Then there are numerous features which depends on how one would want to use it. Overall very satisfied. Not sure if all devices are supported. I had trouble making video calls from my Samsung device as the other person didn't receive my call. The other person was using a Pixel device, that keratin made a video call that i was able to receive and connect.", "It's a very good app, particularly for online meetings and classes. There's one problem with the app that it doesn't work properly with blue tooth speaker, the sound quality and volume, both are not very good with blue tooth speaker. This limits it's usage particularly for classes that require kinesthetic movements like dance, exercise and yoga. Can you please fix this problem?", "I am very pleased with this video app, although I hope you can get a higher definition of quality for the video picture on both ends of the screen. Also, the more special effects, filters, backgrounds, and extras are so much fun and useful in a lot of different ways. Keep up the awesome upgrades! Can't wait for the next new surprises to come ♡♡", "Update: it still is not any better. I did send feedback through the three little dots on meet app. I'm having problems with the picture being fuzzy freezing up. echos when I talk and they are unable to understand me or me them. Can you please look at that. I love the way the app was before. And since we do a lot of face-to-face talking through this app it's really a bummer.", "My partner and I are long distance and have a tendency to go to sleep on call. Despite the fact that we both have full wifi, there have been several occasions where we wake up and the call has ended. Neither of us ended the call, neither of our phones updated, and neither of our apps needed to be updated. Besides that the quality of the calls can be extremely inconsistent, fine one second, grainy, hard to see or hear to frozen video another second. It's inconsistent and just bad.", 'It\'s ok for a video chat app. Main problem is that there isn\'t a button to use the phone speaker. Only Bluetooth on/off, so sound comes out of the phones earpiece only and I can barely hear the other person. The filters are fun, but there\'s just not a lot of what I think are "useful" features. Sometimes I use the children\'s coloring feature as a whiteboard. There\'s no like chat or share features, but not too hard to swap over to text for that. Just an ok app at best, beside that one major issue.', "This has been the most glitchy app I have ever used. I wouldn't expect that coming from Google. If there is a dip in service and it drops the call, I have to restart my phone and not just the app. Half the time, it doesn't hang up and it keeps the call connected while not allowing other calls to come in. My phone is super hot any time I use it. Do better Google", "It was really nice to be able to call with my freinds and family with a face to face experience. I personally have an android so it is one of the only ways I can see freinds and family. The filters and the settings were a bit slow and sometimes didn't load at all, which is a minor issue. Overall, a really good idea, the execution needs some minor adjustments but nothing that won't stop you from conversing woth others.", "When recording videos, now meet automatically lowers the volume of apps that are open. I try recording videos while YouTube music played in the background and it automatically lowers the volume. Also, when this was duo, we were able to zoom in while recording videos and we can no longer do that. Please give us the option to enable these 2 features. I'm in the car audio community so letting my volume while I'm recording videos is really annoying.", "It's a nice app. You can exit out of the app without it kicking you out of the call and there's a share screen option which is nice. But sometimes the audio is pretty bad. Like, I was on a call with my friend and when she said something, a constant beeping sound would play. It was really annoying. And I wish you were able to mute people. Sometimes I'm in big group calls and it's hard to hear others when everyone else was talking.", "The app interface is simple and good looking. I'll be at. I wish the buttons were material you themed also this is the only app I have any issues with the white balance. Quite often the camera blows out and I look like Voldemort and considering this is the only app that does it, it's clearly an issue with the software other than those gripes it's a great app", "It works fine most of the time but sometimes it freezes so much. Even if both users of the call are on full wifi and everything it will glitch and freeze really bad. For long distance relationships and stuff this is a huge inconvenience. It has a lot of trouble connecting sometimes and it won't always show when someone is calling me. These major issues that make the app almost useless sometimes need to be fixed as soon as possible.", 'Updated review: Meet has made some improvements since my last review. Any improvement is welcomed. That said some very basic functions are still missing. Receiving pictures can be difficult if you want to save or copy them. Being able to send or receive notes and or pictures while on an active meet voice call is also missing. Sharing usable hyperlinks is also missing. These simple functions are why nearly all of my colleagues have left the platform. The platform has a lot of potential.', "I've been able to use Meet for audio calls using my Google Mini, Google Nest Display (w/o camera), and video calls using a couple of my phones. I've been able to share photos while in video calls without having to send a separate text message, and the sound has been good I was shocked that the Assistant heard me from a different room than it was in to make a call for me. I am having a problem getting it to connect to my TVs. I'm not sure if available on my Windows 11 laptop yet, but hope so", 'When it was Duo, everything was great. Now I have problems with the volume as it only lowers to a certain point that is still to loud. Also, the brightness does not adjust like it used to. It used to adjust in full darkness for me and the person I was calling. Now it just plunges us into the abyss without any adjustment. I cannot figure out how to fix these after going through absolutely everything.', "I don't know what happened in the last couple of months but I can no longer make calls in this app because I can't verify my phone number. I have tried every step on the help page (force stop, uninstall and reinstall, update phone, restart) multiple times but still nothing. The only thing I use it for is video calls so it's now useless to me.", "I liked duo because it did what I needed. Some of us use Android and some of us use iphone. For the most part it works except when it doesn't, but I think it more my connection. The other thing I don't like is that I cannot change the sound to let me know someone is calling. I barely hear it and miss calls because of that. I try to report the problem but never know if anyone gets it and I NEVER get a response. Gabi", "Hasn't worked since the update. I use this app frequently, and it's tuning into an inconvenience. I go in the app, dial the call, and it just beeps. I was able to answer once, but it never actually opened the call. I have cleared all caches, deleted and reinstalled the app, restarted my phone, nothing.", "I couldn't get any of the calls to connect for over a year. I don't know what happened when it changed from Duo to Meet but that was the last time I used it until now 8/8/23. I erased it and reinstalled it multiple times but still wouldn't work. I had to resort to Facebook Messenger which always worked but the quality of the video calls were hit or miss. I tried Meet today and it worked and was clear. I just hope that it continues to work like it did today, because I prefer it over any other app", "With so many folks caught up in the rat race I think this app is pointless for the most part. There's too many other platforms (usually preloaded on one's device) for use in business and personal affairs. I agree, it's nice to be able to sync a virtual meeting with my email and what not, but sometimes feel overwhelmed with all the Google apps where so much of our personal information is shared.", 'There should be an option for users to change ring tones and notification tones. Besides the ringing not being loud, I need to know which app a call is coming from. By changing the ringtone, I mean having the ability to customize the ringtone with music of my choice. Additionally, when a contact number is opened in the default phone caller, only the video call option is available. There should also be a direct voice option available for contacts saved in the default phone book.', "Great app. I can stay in touch with my hubby with video when he is out of town working. Thanks Duo. I changed my rating for meet because it keeps shutting down. Get video for one second then disappears. Will not stay on, on my Samsung. Can't Uninstall and reinstall. Updated and still doesn't work. Help", "Disappointed 😞! While in a meet, the notification that's showing join and left makes it difficult to exit full screen. And I have waited for half an hour to exit the full screen. After that I found about the long press . So for a newcomer it's so difficult. and it would be a great if you guys can rectify this issue..", "So much better than facetime! We live in the country and have poor internet service. This uses bandwidth much better than FT. Almost no buffering ever when FT won't connect from the same locations. But this app used to be much easier to use when it was DUO. I try to get people to use it but the I vacation set up and first call is seems VERY challenging for people to do. I wonder why Google improved it so badly?!!!", 'The setting for disabling noise cancellation keeps appearing and dissappearing for me. I am so distressed because of this. This is making me drop out of music classes 🥺 Edit 1: I dont see an option of update on play store. So, I am on latest version. I have tried removing cache and storage after stopping the app, and then uninstalling it and installing it afresh. Still dont see a section of audio settings (under which noise cancellation option appears) under my settings.', 'Video constantly switches from wifi to data because of weak signal, but signal is actually strong at 450Mbps. I have to turn my phone to airplane mode to use it. If I start the call on Bluetooth and switch off my headphones the volume is very low and I need to restart the call. Recently there also is an audio delay so conversations are difficult. The app has been unusable because of these things. Previous versions worked fine. This has only been the past few updates.', "Google Duo(Meet),is very clear,with excellent sound quality.It even has evolved better than expected.We use it for family communications,it's certainly very trustworthy,and the simplicity is superb. The support team is also very involved in improvements.5 stars for this App is deserving, against fierce competition, thank you.", "I had to edit my review: For weeks now, I have had constant interruptions during video calls. The person I am talking to can no longer see me and I receive a message that my camera is not available. In addition, the call notification is very unreliable, sometimes even the notification about a missed call is missing. I use the Pixel 7 Pro, so I am particularly irritated by the app's lack of interaction with the phone. In the meantime, I have switched to WhatsApp in frustration.", "It works as well as any other video call app. I don't like the video pre-call screen though. It shows your selfie camera full screen in the background and it looks like I'm already in an active video call or that I'm leaving a video-mail message. I would like it if I could easily distinguish my call status. A flashing red dot or red scrolling/flashing marquee banner across the top of the screen clearly stating the call status, either that you're in a call or that it's ready to make a call. 🎭🎫", 'This being Google I am very disappointed especially when on some devices it is the built-in video calling app used and can\'t be uninstalled. Zoom or similar better performing apps should be studied for "Meet" improvements. Samsung uses this built-in app for communication instead of their original which was much better in all ways. Since this is a built-in Com App, it may be time Google put this app on top of the list for super impressive improvements.', "Sometimes the call will have really bad audio but it's fixed whenever you hang up and call again. Otherwise the app works pretty well. I'm not sure where to put a feature request, but I would like to request a way to lock the screen so that my toddler can't swipe away from the call while he's holding the phone talking to people. Edit: thanks Google for the response. I have a Pixel 7.", "Another absolutely trash phone application for googles own operating system. You cannot minimize yourself at all. I have a folding phone and my own face takes up half the screen when I fold the phone to get a good angle. It's still very bad design and must be intended for narcissists that can't deal with not seeing themselves.", "It is great for video calls and I use it daily. However, there's a forced after-call screen that pops up once I end a call that I made which is extremely annoying. I am quickly moving on to an important notification which made me end the call but I have to see the screen again and then go back to my notification which is the last thing I need in emergencies.", '7/5/2023-I have done all the steps that were mentioned & the app is still not working like it was when myself & 2 additional people are on Meet. The sound is terrible & the picture freezes. I do not have this issue when it is myself & 1 other person. Any other suggestions? Just updated app, can communicate clearly w/ 1 person. However, when trying to connect w/2 people, they can not hear me, and I can not hear them. I can only see them. The app worked fine prior to this last update. Please fix.', "Terrible quality calls. Doesn't know how to register a Bluetooth signal. Randomly dropped calls. Vibrations that don't end even after picking up the call and closing the app. All around a pretty terrible app experience, and genuinely makes me consider buying apple just so I dont have to deal with this."]

title: Talking Puppy
description:
Talking Puppy repeats everything you say with a funny voice. Enjoy hours of fun and laughter with puppy. 

Talking Puppy Features:  
- Talk to puppy and he will repeat everything you say with a funny voice.
- Threw Frisbee to puppy quickly.
- Feed puppy favorite foods, play with him.
- Be a fireman to put out the fire in the city.
- Play mini games with puppy to collect coins.
- Puppy is the monster of circus. 
- Poke his head, arm or feet.
- Have fun with puppy on the playground and make sure he gets some sleep.
- Decorate the puppy's home and collect furniture.
- Customize the puppy by choose from accessories.

Join puppy's world!  Start happy time with your cute puppy!
summary: Talking Puppy repeats everything you say with a funny voice.

title: Dog Shelter Simulator 3D
description:
In the world of Dog Shelter 3D you are an owner of a shelter, where you have to foster dogs and make them happy!

Everytime a new dog comes to your shelter you have to give them food, water, and play with them you have to watch every dog needs!

Sometimes you have to take your dogs to a bath, to make sure everything is perfect!

8 different dog breed waits for you to explore! Upgrade every dog kennel with different items, for example new toys, new beds.

When your dog reach the maximum adopt status you have to adopt them to a loving family!

We hope you will enjoy this experience!
summary: Foster dogs in this shelter simulator experience!

comments: ["This game was surprisingly good for being a mobile game. Though it deffinitly has room to improve! 1. I couldn't name my dogs to adopt (this is my biggest problem) 2. The end activity button was too low on the screen making it hard to press. Positive 1. Fairly good tutoria, I wish there was an option to skip it for those who just don't like tutorials (so me lol) 2. The dogs are adorable, and the movement is fairly good. I do wish the select/grab button was on a different side than the joystick", "This game is a good game, but there's things that make it hard to play and that need improvement. 1. The dogs can get stuck far too easily, and you can't get them unstuck without going to the next day. 2. If you give your dogs food then leave the app because, let's say a dog got stuck, and then come back, the food you gave them is gone but you have to redo the tasks, which I personally don't like. It's a good game, just needs a lot of improvements.", "This game is great! It doesn't have much in app purchases unlike some others I played and the only in app purchases are for gems you can earn for free! Everything else is free too! It's really fun and not that grindy! I love playing this game, it's even offline! Great game for people who don't alannah spend money on a game and is just looking for something to cure boredom :)", "This app is fun but there are some is I have 1. I cannot name my dog so the people don't know what the dog's name is 2. The dogs go through the doors which makes them very hard to catch 3. The dogs are so fast and I having issues putting them in and out of their cages 4. It's unusual to let dogs go around without permission and 5. I have a little a bit of issues because the cages only are two so I can't get more dogs if you guys fix it I will be happy to play it", "This game isn't too bad. The joystick is a little weird, also if I accidentally click off naming for the dog, I can't name them. Lastly, the camera. Please fix it. You can't take pictures or get off the camera if you click on it. Please fix these and I will re download.", "So I love the idea of this game but here's the issue first of all it's very confusing if I don't know how to do something I can't get help or skill that part! For example one of the dogs needed to go to the clinic so I took it there it said that it needed inspection so I gave it inspection and it didn't let me go farther than that every time I did the inspection it either said quick inspection and so I would but it wouldn't let me treat it. Plz help!!!", "Absolutely fantastic game ever I can't stop playing it also I was thinking of things you should add when dogs are getting a bath could you add shampoo or a dog cap for his ears that would be adorable otherwise Please keep the game the same as it is if anyone is ready this please install this game it's absolutely amazing also they game has my dog in it :) amazing game 5 stars👍", 'this is a great game! totally love this, but it gets boring when you play for some time :< but I still recommend the game for some pet lovers out there :>. I will look forward for the next update!!', "I HATE IT. I can never find out how to set the dogs down and never get rid ball. And the dogs look crusty. It's just bad quality 😕 I have to go to a certain spot to put the dog down but it's so hard to find", "Amazing game!! I love it!! It's a really cool game with cute animals. But the only thing is that there's not much to do. You do the same thing all day everyday in the game. But beside that, it's a good game!! I would recommend playing this!", "It's so cute and fun but could u add cats maybe u could upgrade the kennels more but it's great keep working hard! :D and thank you for not giving up stay strong!", "This game is really good too learn how to work at shelters I don't know if everyone agrees with me but my only complaint is that in the middle of the game it glitches and it's all skipy but ya pretty good for your own kids", "Pretty Cool But Has Not Alot But Most Of The Time Ads. To Get Rid Of Them Just Turn Off Your Internet And You'll Be Good. The Graphism Aren't The Best But It's Ok. Keep Going Developers! 👍🏽✨", "I think it is a great game it has a few ads but that's how we paying the game and they've not a big varity of options in the game but it's a wonderful game none the less", 'How do you clean the cages? And i wish you could do more like maybe have "helpers", add in more kennels etc. I enjoy this game alot just id love to see more added into it', "It is a good game but it is laggy but I am a dog lover so yeah and it is such a cute game and I love the dogs and I joined 7 days ago and I am already in love I don't know why but it is awesome I only get an ad when I shut the computer but the thing is I don't know how to clean", "The game is fun I played this game for 7 days and I am already in love with it 8 am a puppy lover and don't believe people that say there is to many ads it is a lie", 'So fun but I feel like it needs more things to do since it gets a bit boring', 'I like this game but the dogs get stuck to easily Could you maybe make a horse shelter simulator pls', "This game is extremely nice If there is any problems with it I still love it causes I'm an animal lover.I recommend it to anyone who loves animals.🥰😍😘💖", "It won't let me download it and I seen it for my favorite YouTubers play it and I really wanted to play it but it looks like a good game but probably might be but I doubt it", 'I like the game but I dont know how to get your dog adopted I watched the into but it didnt say. But other than that the game is fantastic', "It's good but it never told me how to pickup the pet beucouse there was no jump", "I loved this experience it,s lots of fun there's nothing you need to change about it it,s just amazing", "This game has a lot of potential it just hasn't reached it (I would like it to have more details and etc)", 'The game is amazing 💕 but the graphics need a little help 👁👄👁', "I hafe 5 comments 1.i love taking care of animals so this is perfect for me 2.cute dog's 3.good graphics 4.no glitch and 5.does not kick you out of the game", "I love this game too so much I have a dog too I love this game so much because I'm a kid and kids love other games and dogs are my special thing to do I love to play with them and cuddling with them it's like this is my special game", 'I love this game but one little problem is that it glitches so fix this glitch please', "Rip-off of the real game you can't put the dog down and you can't even hold the water the quality is trash", 'Great but a little bit tricky for me to figure out how to get toys and beds', 'Kept glitching and way to many ads.', 'I saw it on cookie sworl cs cannle an i went to play it its a really fun game and there is a cat named cat i love this game its really cool cheek it out', 'It fun but hard to get more dogs after u get dot and bot', 'This game is awful, it would not load, I never got to play it, not right,fix it', "Because dogs are my favorite animal and they're really adorable in the game and in real life", 'Can you add more things like building and stuff because I hate boring games', "I really love this game it's so much fun and it makes me so happy 😍.", 'Lovely there are many glitches for the dryer tho.', 'Oh this game is so much interest I like so much but update cats and we walk outside update plz']

title: My Virtual Pet Shop: Animals
description:
Do you love animal games? So, download now My Virtual Pet Shop to take care of fluffy dogs and cats! Join 820k animal lovers on the best puppy pet care games for kids!
Welcome to your new pet shop! Build your own pet store and take care of cute animals while customers visit your shop. Play, groom, feed, bathe, groom and dress up kittens and puppies to keep the dogs and cats happy! My Virtual Pet Shop is so much fun, play now! This pet cares game is very exciting, if you love dogs and cats, My Virtual Pet Shop by Tapps Games is made especially for you! Take good care of cute animals and show them how much you love them! By taking great care of the cute animals in your pet shop, you'll level up and earn lots of coins at the end of every day. With these coins, unlock items and improve your virtual animals store, customize your tools to take even better care of the dogs and cats, and make your customers very happy! My Virtual Pet Shop Game by Tapps Games is one of the cutest games you will ever play! Get ready to see cute kittens and puppies from all kinds of breeds and show how much you love cute animals! ANIMAL CARE CUTE GAMES Fun and cute games to take care of dogs, cats and all animals, this game will make your days at my pet shop even more exciting. You’ll simply adore this cat and dog game. ★ Wash the puppies and kittens in your professional bathtub – Grab a sponge, some shampoo and with lots of love, wash every pet that comes to your animal store. ★ Play Dress Up – Make dogs and cats super stylish by accessorizing them with cute accessories! They are going to be so cute! ★ Eliminate fleas from the puppies and kittens – Eliminate these insects from your dogs and cats to guarantee them plenty of comfort. HIGHLIGHTS IN THIS CAT AND DOG GAME This vet game has many fun activities to take care of animals, but among them, these are the highlights: ★ Four different activities to take care of the pets: animal spa, dress up the animals, bathe and groom the animals in your pet salon. ★ Play this pet cares game in a simple way: this animal game is very easy to play, you just need to LOVE pet games and take good care of all animals, cats, dogs, kittens and puppies! ★ Upgradable Items: Upgrade my pet shop by earning daily coins and buying better equipment. ★ The fun in my virtual pet shop is fast-paced and challenging: play dog and cat mini games and become a real pet salon and vet owner. A VET CUTE GAME In my virtual pet shop, you won't just make animals cute, did you know that? From your ninth day of playing my virtual pet, you can be a veterinarian! Apply vaccines, medicines and make sure the animals are in great health condition! You’ll nurse dogs, cats, puppies and kittens back to health. LEVELS IN THIS CAT AND DOG GAME Be prepared for new challenges as you'll start serving more demanding clients and taking care of multiple animals at the same time! Can you handle it? Heads up! This cute game by Tapps Games is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and extra items mentioned in the description can also be purchased for real money.
summary: Take care of Cute Animals, like Dogs, Cats & Rabbits. Pet Shop Simulator Game!

comments: ["The game is quite enjoyable. Can be played offline. Mini games are fun and the pace isn't boring or overwhelming. I wish the pets weren't so impatient. Pets lose patience even when playing mini games. Also I wish upgrades didn't take so long to finish. Can't upgrade more than one equipment as well. A storyline would also be a great bonus.", "The game is really fun. The only problem is you have to watch ads for everything If you wanna collect your coins, you're watching an ad. If you wanna upgrade something, you have to watch an ad.", "It's enjoyable but the pets lose patience for about seconds that you didn't move them. You can only upgrade one at a time, if you want to finish it you have to use stars which is sometimes not enough for the upgrade. Upgrades took so much time.", "Really cute and simple game, but I feel like the pets lose patience really fast, like if they're not in the seat in five seconds then their patience drops. Also, it's kinda dumb to have to wait for an upgrade to finish before starting a new one. Why can't we just wait on multiple? Cute game but some of its workings are dumb.", "So fun! I love the game so much! At times, it gets hard and you get a B ranking. I don't mind it though, great game! I recommend. Not too many ads, perfect for road trips/in the car! Play it almost 24/7.", "I wish I could give this no stars! It wouldn't even let me play!! Every time I try to open the game it gives m an error. I tried downloading and unstalling time and time again but every time he gives me the same error. I loved this game as a child please fix :(", 'I rate 3/4 because this game is quite enjoyable, but not relaxing. It really needs improvement. Although, you can play it offline the pets are very impatient and the game looks pretty old.', "this game is very fun to play for when you are bored or don't have anything to do the graphics are so clear and amazing 🤩 and the animals are so adorable to sum it up I recommend this game to anyone who likes pets ⭐", "There is just too many ads. If I wanted to watch that much of videos I would've opened YouTube (: It's called game for a reason.. So people could play with it, not watch videos for like every two minutes", "So far, I really like the game. It's not boring nor its promising. Recommend this game for children ages 3-5. My niece really like this game since its not difficult for them to understand the concept of the game. Kudos to the creator. 💓", 'Cute, but not challenging enough. Hate how I had to wait for upgrades and how I can only upgrade only one item at a time. Uninstalled.', 'Offline straight forward gameplay. Easy-to-grasp concept. Quite simple. Limited in-game updates.', "Super cute and fun! Also can be addicting But i don't like the way we the pets lose patience really fast like why can't they wait? I mean we don't have space but it's very fun:))", "I think it would be better if the mini game that you wash the pet didn't take so long and it was like the fleas mini game bcz then it would be more fun", "the game's design is very cute and the overall gameplay is very easy and fun, it's perfect for relaxing", "eventually you'll have 2 days wait time for upgrades. the 30 second ads remove only 1 hour of wait time. this comes out to watching 48 ads.. so you will get to a point where you either hqve to spend money or wait 2 days for one single upgrade because you can only upgrade 1 thing at a time. its a shame because its actually a very fun and cute multitasking game.", "I absolutely love this game, it's so fun! I think the amount of time it takes for new upgrades to load should be shortened though.", "I really like this game a lot because I could play it whenever i'm bored and just want to get some stuff of my head I play this game there is rarely ads and its so cute!", "I love it ...I downloaded it a yesterday and it's so addicting I can't stop playing it the grafics are amazing and the animals are so cute amazing game for sure !!", "TY for moving bundle ad...but this game requires money or watching a gazillion ads, and when you've maxed out upgrades it's more boring....", 'kinda hard when u need to open the tip jar but needs an ad to run.. but nonetheless, the game itself is great !!', "I love this game it's fun, nice and adorable but I don't like when you can't buy the items at ones", "I'm 5 years old and play with my pa pa and it's the best game I've ever played. keeps me playing and can't wait to play next time I'm allowed", "It's not the best game but it is cool when I'm bored . And the graphics are well done so I give it 4 stares! (*0*)", 'Hi, i love this game and it is really fun. When i finished a day around i saw a text and i should rate it and tell you how to make it better and i have an idea. The idea is you see when your level 9 you have the food so i think you should design it with 2 pets eating and the candle that you have on level 14 you should design it with 2 pets really want to touch it. So thats it i hope people like it.', "I had a good rating on this game, but restoring purchases doesn't work. So money wasted. I hate this game now.", "Great game! The pets are so cute 🥺 and the gameplay is easy enough without being boring! I've played this game twice now and am playing it again that's how amazing it is! I'd recommend checking it out if you love animals 😻 The only thing I would say is as you get more items the wait time increases and that can be annoying as you can only buy one thing at a time. Maybe we could watch a certain amount of ads to hurry up the time? just a suggestion 😸", "Great game! Personally, I think the creators could add maybe one or two more areas like a feeding station and maybe even an exercise station just to extend the game time once you've brought all the upgrades, but again it's just a thought. :) I also think maybe you could add a minigame for each station for the people, like me, who do like a little challenge now and again. I would definitely like to see them in the game in future, but other than that, amazing game!👍🏻❤️", "ad's, I can completely understand some of them like for: speed up, double reward and etc, some random ones once in a while too, but when just trying to get after ending game to another level I get 6 ad's it's not okay. And I would let it slide if that would happen like once, fine will wait those ad's, but when it's every single time it's way to much. I hope it will get better in future. Also animal mood change is way to fast. Overall its good game to pass time.", "I personally love this game! I used to hate it as a kid because it was hard, but now i know how to multitask. Only down side in my opinion is it takes really long to get the upgrades. I wouldn't mind it if you can get off and let time go, but that doesn't seem to work for me and you have to level up to get the tokens and eventually ( im on like level 32 ) leveling up gets really hard, and its almost a requirment to use money. Despite that, I'll keep playing. Btw 3rd building should be a zoo", "So everything with this game was cute and fun and I was able to play for a day or so but my issue is that the game forces you to watch a 30 second ad after every level you complete and a level only takes a minute to finish. So lots of ads and that's really annoying. I don't mind the choice of watching an ad for double coins but forcing ads on top of that gets frustrating. Besides that the controls were easy, the rules were simple, and for some reason I was addicted to taking the fleas off.", 'This has always been my favorite game, but what makes me gave it a low star is every after game there will be ads, most of it my screen will just turn black and i have no choice but to close it and open again only to find out that i lost the previous level (though i completed it) and whatever i purchased, earned on that level, sad part is you will see your coins deducted from the previous purchase. Please fix this. Update: Kudos in fixing the issue! Installed it again for my kids to play it.', "Super cute and perfectly challenging. I'm able to skip the occasional ads between levels, and there isn't an overwhelming amount of ads. Very easy to progress the basic game without spending real money, especially if you watch ads to spend things up. It's a great time killer. Keep up the good work!", "Great game but glitching with bonuses! I love the game and it's really cute, however whenever I try to watch an ad to get a bonus like the cookies or double coins the app will close out and act as though I never watch the ad and I'll never get the bonus. It makes it really annoying because without the extra bonuses it's very hard to get ahead on some of the things.", "First of all I love this game because it makes my day better and because of this I won't be able to get bored. Thank you so much developer for making this game, and I would like to recommend this to everyone. ♥", 'It is perfectly fine but the pets kept coming again again before compliting the one.', "I love this game I'm really picky about animal caregiver games, so this is an awesome game.", "♡My favourite game out there! So cute and fun😄 , notably not boring! SO nice, it is amazing! Downlad/ install now. ( ✌︎'ω')✌︎", "I love this game so much but I don't think the animals should get bored/mad so quickly", "It is so fun to play except it has ads but it's still fun anyways"]

title: My Cat - Virtual pet simulator
description:
Have you been dreaming of getting a pet? Your dreams are coming true with My Cat. Get a kitty with the cutest pet simulator ever.

Meet your new virtual fluffy friend in simulation games. Just look into these honest cats eyes. They are melting your heart already, right? Now you can listen to its happy pleasant purr-purr engine all day long. Play with your little kitten, give it the most delicious yummies, take it for a walk and have fun every day. Our cat game is made for joy. Love your cat and it will love you back 😻

The only virtual cat that looks like and feels like a real cat. Oh, those charming cat manners. Kitten games will make you laugh every day and will become your best friend. You can even say “This is my talking pet”. It is so amazing to play with a tamagotchi cat. Take your kitty wherever you want, it is always by your side. You’ll always have fun with your fluffy friend.

Your purring digital pet needs your love and attention. Discover the My Cat’s adventure world.

MY CAT GAME FEATURES

🎮 AUGMENTED REALITY. Use your smartphone camera and your virtual cat will appear right in your house or wherever you want. Cat games for girls and boys can do it now. You will love it.
📸 FUNNY MEMORIES. Take cute photos of your talking cat to share with friends and show off on social media.
🎁 EXTRA ITEMS. Take care of a cat, play with it, and enjoy extra items as a reward.
💓 SO REAL. Cats react to your every touch. Stroke it or scratch its cute little nose with your finger. It is so easy to turn on your kitty’s purring engine.
🐈 MORE FUN. While your virtual pet is asleep or occupied with some important cat business you can set new records in an exciting animal Match 3 games or mini games. Challenge yourself and set your own records.

Show everyone how adorable your kitten is with our pet simulator. Сatch cat adventure, how cat talk, play, and all the moments spent together with your tamagochi friend. Take amusing and memorable selfies with your AR cat and collect them in the photo gallery. But don't let your cute little virtual cat wait for too long. Cat games  made for fun. Everyone loves playing My Cat. Kid games for girls and boys are teaching them how to take care of a real baby cat. They can learn a lot through playing.

👑PREMIUM ACCESS IN GAMES👑
Subscribe for Premium and get unlimited access to all the game features:

⭐️ Unlock all premium items
⭐️ Unlock AR mode
⭐️ Free daily coins and diamonds

It is your time to get a talking cat and make your dream come true. Give it all your love and you will have the most faithful fluffy tamagotchi friend ever. Enjoy playing with My Cat virtual kitty. 💟
summary: AR tamagotchi with kitten! Take care & raise kitty cat and play mini games

comments: ["this game is adorable but allow me to save you the heartache. it's gonna cost you $10 a week to keep playing this game. just downloaded it and start the game. it'll tell you right before you start playing that it's a 3 day free trial. now I'm not sure how to make sure I don't get charged. do I just uninstall or will it still charge me if I uninstall but don't cancel somehow? I didn't sign up and I don't want charged?", "Very shady. Vip subscription popup first, infested with packs every time you exit the part of a screen. In addition, you have to pay for an item to be only used once??? I'll go play my talking Tom/Angela instead. Edit: What i mean by buying one-use items is by in-game currency, not real money.", 'I just saw this game, read the reviews and decided to check if everything is so bad. I would say that the game is quite acceptable, quite good, the children will like it. Of course there are a lot of ads and as another dude said, paid content that is easy to connect which is not very good when children play it and ruin their parents themselves without realizing it. Like Tamagotchi, standard, quite cute and just not a bad game.', 'what the heck!? it\'s not even letting you play. after downloading, took me to subscription page. you should give the people the option to be "VIP member" or just regular players. thought it was free to play, but no! it\'s like this app is forcing you to PAY PER WEEK to play!', "My child accidentally installed this game from an advertisement and bought a weekly subscription for an exorbitant amount. Fortunately I could quickly cancel the subscription and change the purchase settings on my child's device. It is clear that these greedy apps are just taking advantage of young children and rubbish purchase default settings. I'm disgusted with the unscrupulous nature of these companies.", "So many ads even after paying for no ads. I got this game for my 4 year old and he kept having trouble with ads so I payed for them to be removed, but still he kept being presented with ads and being taken our of the game. Your platforms are scummy and you're just trying to trick kids into downloading as many of your bad games by roping them in with you ads. DO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS FOR YOU CHILDREN.", "My 2yr old daughter accidentally purchase this app. please help, is there a way I can be refunded for this? I tried on Google play but somehow it was declined. 500php is really a big amount for just a game she doesn't want to play either. please help", "so cute! I am going to play this game everyday, every hour I get! The basic idea is that you get to take care of a virtual kitty pet that is so cute! I mean, I can't even take it!", 'So chock full of ads. No joke, every 25 seconds there is an ad to watch and wade through. Do NOT leave your kids unattended with this game. It repeatedly prompts to subscribe to something in-game, for OVER $20 PER WEEK. The developers should be ashamed of themselves.', "super slow and glitchy. it could have just been the phone though. other than that it's a cute game😊", "Nice game, it took me forever to choose ONE of the three cats offered at the start of the game! They are all so adorable I wished there was a button that would let me take them all. Too bad there's a subscription tied to this game. Also the cat's noises are too human and there is one screeching noise it often does which makes me worried if it's choking or dying. The sound just doesn't make sense.", 'Might as well make us buy the game since we cant play without paying 10 dollars a month. You trick people into downloading your game thinking it was free to play but its not.', "Within the first seconds my son got an ad of a subscription he needed to pay for 17.99€. A WEEKLY SUBSCRIPTION. He accidentally bought it because he can't read yet and tried to close it while i forgot to put him back in kids mode. I thankfully got a refund. no where here this is mentioned. Absolutely disgusting.", 'Horrible. I paid for no ads and I still get ads, fix this! I hate having my toddler dealing with invasive ads and she still gets them! I just wanted my money', 'I was surprised when I saw payments of €10.99 coming out of my account without my authorization on a monthly basis. My 6 year old daughter innocently started playing this game not realizing that there is a subscription charge. How can Google let this happen. Ban apps like these!!!', 'I like the way that the cat reacts to everything you do for him or her. I will play it alot! So thanks you so much for making this game! Biggest smiles and claps!!!', "Just wanna share how my 3 year old daughter were able to subscribe to te VIP of this app so easily. It's frustrating that google doesn't even do refunds.!!!", 'Really good, my 7 year old loves this game and the instructions are straight forward and easy to follow.', "Currently stuck on screen this is congratulations wow someone's outgrown their old things!? Was a 1% bar underneath it that has been stuck at 1% for like 3 days I'm probably going to uninstall and reinstall to see if that fixes it", "Don't download. Starts with glitchy sounds that crackle my phone speakers and goes in and out, then first thing that pops up is an huge 'ad' telling me to agree to pay a huge amount of money to just play the game!! I didn't even get to experience anything first. Automatically 0 stars. Since I backed out when the game froze while telling me to pay to play, I don't have any opinions on anything else. Didn't waste my time further, I suggest you don't either.", 'Immediately hit with paywall that was not able to be skipped... 19.99/week is ridiculous. There are better games for less. Do better.', 'I LOVE THE GAME!!!!!When i find this game i go on play store and install it.Is a veryyyy fun game.Also for persons ho want a cat but they are not shure,this game is perfect for them.You can also see what a cat do 24h.Is good for kids because they learn how to take care of a cat.', "Terrible It claims free with in app purchases but the first thing that pops up says 14.99/week and you can't get out of it!", "Couldn't get past the screen that says you have to pay 14.99 a week to play the game. Thats an outrageous price for a game.", "Can't even play it without paying £8 per week. Absolute rip off and a complete waste of time.", "My daughter downloaded this app and suddenly I had a charge for £8,49 for a weekly VIP subscription on my card. I just can't imagine how easy this app allows these sort of transactions, she's 5 years old and clearly pressed keys withouth knowing that she was accepting an in app purchase. I still wonder how that happened as it was allowed without password, verifications or submitting security info such as cvv for the card. I cancelled and unsubscribed straight away and Google play refuses refund", 'How do you even skip the VIP subscription screen. I thought it was free with ads?', 'Horrible,My Daughter got this game and they tricked her into charging my card ! I have no received a refund or anything I quickly unsubscribed but still no refund this is Terrible I hate it.', 'too poor a lot of ads than the actual simulation play', "It took forever to pick One cat but I managed to pick one and the game is a five stars at the best game I've ever seen", 'too many ads for other games and bundles..', "it's so fun I absolutely love how you can photo it into you house it has so cute sound affects like when it pees . It is so fun I think every one should get it. 🥰😍🤩🥰😛👍🏽👍🏽👍🏽👍🏽👍🏽👍🏽🤑🤑👍🏽🤑👍🏽🤑👍🏽👍🏽🍰👍🏽🤑👍🏽", "How does this even get 4 stars? My kid asked if he could add it. I saw it was FREE and said sure. 5 minutes later I get an email saying I'm paying $16/week for a subscription to play it. I saw another 'add on' for like $64. You guys have some kind of scam going here in hoping parents don't notice the purchase or something. Google won't be happy with the refunds and take you down soon enough.", 'This app is a hoax. Everyone can accidentally purchase a VIP weekly subscription without any password or credentials... I have registered payment method and before the purchase I have to confirm the payment with my credentials. This app can somehow push through the payment process without any confirmation. And of course the refund is not possible. Google must check or ban this app!!!', "I did like the game but u have to wait for the ads and it did not make me mad at all but i didn't like it but the game was really cute and nice though", 'Downloaded this game for my daughter realized not even 24 hours later that she was just clicking buy the subscription and other this apparently bc I have a $60 charge. They will cancel my subscription, but not give me a refund! Guess thats how they make their money. Watch if your cards are connected!!', "it is the best game ever I play it when Im bored and when I don't see my cat outside it looks just like my cat too", "Frustrated,how it come that this game is no safeguard about paying even the child didn't intend to purchase items,very child friendly on purchasing a very nice way to earn money by the developer.", 'To avoid not disappointing your child, do not download this. It opens and lets you select a kitten. Fun right? Things are going great. Oh wait. You have to pay money to get beyond that point and actually play the game. This tricky nonsense is wrong.', "The cat is soooo cute 🥰 but here's the problem: at first you get a free 3 day trial, then you need to get coins in the game to buy stuff, and you only have it once!
